“我本是男儿郎”
I am by nature a boy...

188
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:39,230
嗯
What?

189
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:40,030
“我…”
I...

190
00:17:40,230 --> 00:17:42,180
“我本是…男儿郎”
I am by nature a boy...

191
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:46,010
你本是女娇娥
You are by nature a girl!

192
00:17:46,010 --> 00:17:47,970
我需要你错…你错
Can't you see you're wrong!

193
00:17:48,210 --> 00:17:50,540
啊 我打你个小癞子
I'll punish you, Laizi!

194
00:17:50,660 --> 00:17:51,410
打
Punish you!

195
00:17:51,840 --> 00:17:52,580
打
Punish you!

196
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:55,190
你还错 你要干嘛
You still can't get it right, can you?

197
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:56,390
你怎么唱的
How did you sing it?

198
00:17:56,760 --> 00:17:58,200
小癞子再也不敢了
Don't hit me! I won't do it again!

199
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:58,880
再打
Again hit!

200
00:18:02,850 --> 00:18:04,040
你的“思凡”
Sing "Dreaming of the World Outside the Nunnery".

201
00:18:04,370 --> 00:18:10,540
“本是…我本是…我本是…我本是…”
I am... I am by nature...

202
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,260
你本是什么呀 啊
Spit it out!

203
00:18:14,910 --> 00:18:16,880
“我本是 男儿郎”
I am by nature a boy...

204
00:18:17,220 --> 00:18:19,510
尼姑是男的 还是女的
Is a nun male or female?

205
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:23,350
是…男儿郎
A boy.

206
00:18:24,420 --> 00:18:26,960
您倒是真入了化境了
You really are in character.

207
00:18:27,480 --> 00:18:29,670
连雌雄都不分了 啊
You can't even tell male from female.

208
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:42,140
“我…”
I...

209
00:18:42,680 --> 00:18:43,400
“我…”
I...

210
00:18:44,050 --> 00:18:45,010
“我本是…”
I am...

211
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,500
“男儿郎”
...by nature a boy

212
00:18:48,410 --> 00:18:50,200
师傅说的戏 你全忘了
You've forgotten everything the master has taught you!

213
00:18:50,390 --> 00:18:51,430
下次再忘
Do it again,

214
00:18:51,780 --> 00:18:53,090
就往死里打你
and I'll beat you to within an inch of your life.

215
00:18:53,410 --> 00:18:55,130
让你错 我让你错
Wrong! Wrong!

216
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:56,590
让你错 让你...
Wrong...

217
00:18:56,710 --> 00:18:58,990
小子 长点记性
You'd better remember this.

218
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:05,480
磨剪子来
Bring your knives for sharpening!

219
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:10,550
镪菜刀
Sharpen your knives!

220
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:27,080
师哥
Bro.

221
00:19:28,410 --> 00:19:29,850
赶明儿 我要是给打死了
If by chance I'm beaten to death tomorrow,

222
00:19:31,840 --> 00:19:33,290
枕席底下 有三大子儿
I want you to have the three copper coins...

223
00:19:34,610 --> 00:19:35,620
就给你了
...hidden under my mattress.

224
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:40,680
留神
Careful!

225
00:19:42,670 --> 00:19:43,600
别进水
Don't let it touch the water.

226
00:19:44,810 --> 00:19:46,510
手毁了 就唱不了戏了
If you ruin your hand, forget acting.

227
00:19:55,370 --> 00:19:56,110
豆子
Douzi,

228
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:59,040
过两天 就要给祖师爷上香了
Douzi, in a few days, you'll be initiated into the troupe.

229
00:19:59,540 --> 00:20:01,580
你就想你自己是个女的
You can think of yourself as a girl,

230
00:20:02,230 --> 00:20:03,770
可别再背错了
just don't stuff up the lyrics again.

231
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:19,700
癞子
Laizi,

232
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,040
吃过豌豆黄吗
Laizi, have you ever eaten sweet pea cakes?

233
00:20:21,220 --> 00:20:24,190
豌豆黄 豌豆黄算个屁呀
What's the big deal about sweet pea cakes?

234
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:25,560
吃过驴打滚吗
Have you ever had "Thrashing Donkey" millet rolls?

235
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:26,540
盆儿糕呢
"Basin cakes"?

236
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:29,260
都是他妈狗屁 不好吃
They're about as fucking special as dog farts.

237
00:20:29,410 --> 00:20:30,780
那你说什么好吃啊
So what do you like?

238
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:38,490
天下最好吃的 冰糖葫芦数第一
There's nothing yummier than a stick of candied crab-apples.

239
00:20:39,010 --> 00:20:40,410
我要是成了角儿
If I make it big,

240
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:43,220
天天得拿冰糖葫芦当饭吃
I'll eat candied crab-apples every day for dinner.

241
00:20:44,350 --> 00:20:55,830
“冰糖葫芦 冰糖葫芦”
Candied crab-apples for sale!

242
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:58,540
甭这么瞧着朕
Don't look at us like that,

243
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:01,250
朕又不是冰糖葫芦
we're not a stick of candied crab-apples!

244
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:05,370
癞子 哈喇子都流出来了
Laizi, you're drooling!

245
00:21:14,700 --> 00:21:15,500
你嘛呢你
What the hell are you doing?

246
00:21:15,970 --> 00:21:18,240
- 回来 - 这么大个儿的风筝 一堆呢
- Get back here. - Wow, such big kites, and so many of them!

247
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,590
快回去 回去
Come back!

248
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,460
小豆子
Douzi!

249
00:21:41,150 --> 00:21:41,910
快跑
Run for it!

250
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,220
跑了一个
Run a man.

251
00:21:44,880 --> 00:21:45,710
站住
Hold it right there!

252
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:52,340
小豆子
Douzi!

253
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,380
师哥
Bro.

254
00:21:56,210 --> 00:21:57,620
枕席底下 那三大子儿
Don't forget the copper cash...

255
00:21:58,450 --> 00:21:59,250
你别忘了
...under my mattress.

256
00:22:07,120 --> 00:22:08,190
反正你废了
You're worthless.

257
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:10,640
滚吧
Get out of my sight!

258
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:23,110
诶 哪儿来的
Hey, where'd you get that?

259
00:22:23,410 --> 00:22:24,890
你那三大子儿买的啊
I bought it with your three copper coins.

260
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:28,240
小石头甭想花了 让朕受用了吧
Stuff Shitou, I'm spending your money now.

261
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:30,560
诶 一串十个 我给你俩怎么样
Ten apples on each stick. I'll give you two. How about it?

262
00:22:32,010 --> 00:22:32,910
你怎么了 你啊
What's with you?

263
00:22:32,910 --> 00:22:33,890
我憋了泡尿
I have to pee real bad.

264
00:22:34,210 --> 00:22:35,790
诶 大街上可不许撒尿
You can't do it in the middle of the street.

265
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,020
靠边点 靠边点诶
Come on!

266
00:22:37,870 --> 00:22:38,960
哎哟 王老板
It's Manager Wang!

267
00:22:39,770 --> 00:22:41,670
角儿来了 角儿来了
The stars have arrived!

268
00:22:42,290 --> 00:22:43,580
这儿有近道 走近道
Here, come this way.

269
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:55,380
哎哟 我的角儿诶 您这可是星宿下凡啦
Oh, my dear sir, this is indeed like a visitation from heaven!

270
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:02,910
您今儿就一声喷嚏 也得是满堂彩儿
All you need do is sneeze and you get a standing ovation.

271
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:05,210
您受累了
We've put you to so much trouble.

272
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:11,630
今天不挤出几条人命 就上上大吉了
It'll be pure luck if no one is trampled to death in there!

273
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:44,530
诶 你先驮着我 待会儿我驮着你呀
I'll sit on your shoulders for a while, then you sit on mine.

274
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:54,260
霸王 霸王诶
It's the king!

275
00:24:24,370 --> 00:24:26,170
他们怎么成的角儿啊 
What does it take to become a star?

276
00:24:28,930 --> 00:24:30,640
得挨多少打啊
How many beatings?

277
00:24:32,160 --> 00:24:33,880
得挨多少打啊
How many beatings?

278
00:24:36,290 --> 00:24:38,500
我什么时候才能成角儿啊
When will we ever enjoy such fame?

279
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:16,240
- 诶 不 - 怎么意思诶
- No. - What's this?

280
00:25:16,420 --> 00:25:18,300
你怎么尿我一脸呀你
You're pissing all over my face!

281
00:25:20,250 --> 00:25:21,380
干嘛呀 你
What the hell are you doing?

282
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:34,690
我就知道 你要回来
I knew you'd want to go back.

283
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:37,120
离了小石头 你就活不了啦
You couldn't live without Shitou!

284
00:25:37,800 --> 00:25:40,340
回去 你又得挨刀胚子
You're going to get a taste of the sword.

285
00:25:40,740 --> 00:25:41,880
我可是不怕
Personally, I'm not afraid.

286
00:25:42,370 --> 00:25:43,880
早就打皮实了
I've been beaten so much I'm tough as nails,

287
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:46,380
师傅打我 就跟挠痒痒似的
it's like having an itch scratched.

288
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,030
吃了糖葫芦
I've eaten my candied crab-apples.

289
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:49,440
我就是他妈角儿了
I'm a fucking star already!

290
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:51,320
我能怕谁啊
Who the hell do I have to be afraid of?

291
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:58,900
好小子 你们还回来呀 哪里跑
You little scamps, you've come back after all.

292
00:26:01,130 --> 00:26:02,340
打得好 打得好
Good! I deserve it!

293
00:26:02,340 --> 00:26:09,160
反了你了 叫你开门放人…
Why the hell did you let them go?

294
00:26:09,960 --> 00:26:11,330
我打死你啊
I've had it with you!

295
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:20,970
背班逃跑者 罚
Skipping class and running away must be punished!

296
00:26:23,130 --> 00:26:24,890
师傅 别打了 师傅 诶 师傅
Master, I'll never do it again.

297
00:26:26,000 --> 00:26:27,290
下次再也不饶了我
Master, I'll never do it again. Please let me go!

298
00:26:28,320 --> 00:26:29,580
你竟然跑
How dare you run

299
00:26:30,710 --> 00:26:31,580
不要打豆子
Don't hit Douzi.

300
00:26:32,880 --> 00:26:37,290
我叫你开门放人 你就放人 我打死你
Who told you to let them go? I'll kill you!

301
00:26:37,460 --> 00:26:38,550
抓住他 抓住他
Catch him! Catch him!

302
00:26:39,450 --> 00:26:42,190
师傅 你饶了我 下次再也不敢了
Master, I'll never do it again. Please let me go!

303
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:43,560
饶了我吧 师傅
Master, Please let me go!

304
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:51,050
师傅
Master,

305
00:26:52,180 --> 00:26:53,860
是我自个儿跑的
Master, it was me who ran away.

306
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,160
不关师哥的事
He didn't have anything to do with it.

307
00:26:58,090 --> 00:26:58,970
您打我
Beat me instead!

308
00:27:38,170 --> 00:27:39,450
我叫你跑
I told you to run.

309
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:40,930
你有...
You..

310
00:27:41,740 --> 00:27:43,050
我打死你
I'll kill you.

311
00:27:44,060 --> 00:27:45,330
打死你呀
Kill you ah!

312
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:47,440
你以为我不敢打你呀
Did you think you wouldn't get yours?

313
00:28:00,290 --> 00:28:01,770
你当我不打你
Did you think you wouldn't get yours?

314
00:28:02,040 --> 00:28:03,470
我打死你
I'll kill you.

315
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:08,560
豆子 说呀 说呀 开口呀
Douzi, speak! Say something!

316
00:28:08,860 --> 00:28:11,240
讨个饶呀 说打得好呀 说呀
Beg for mercy! Say he's beaten you well and truly!

317
00:28:11,250 --> 00:28:14,700
我打死你 你跑 你跑
I'll kill you! Run away, will you?

318
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,950
开口 说呀
Speak!

319
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:17,890
打死你
I'll beat you to death if I must.

320
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:21,050
打死你 咱们散伙儿
I'll beat you to death if I must. Let's just disband the troupe...

321
00:28:21,640 --> 00:28:22,320
打
Beat!

322
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,270
打死你
I'll beat you to death if I must.

323
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:29,900
你把小豆子打死了
You're killing Douzi!

324
00:28:34,940 --> 00:28:36,280
我跟你拼了
I won't let you do this!

325
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:47,070
关爷 关爷 可了不得了
Master Guan! Something terrible has happened!

326
00:28:47,310 --> 00:28:48,730
这个 他…死了
Laizi, he...died.

327
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:45,960
“霸王别姬”
"Farewell My Concubine"

328
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:49,450
讲的是楚汉相争的故事
tells the story of the struggle between the Chu and Han kings.

329
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:53,400
楚霸王 何许人也
What sort of man was the King Of Chu?

330
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:58,000
那是天下无敌的盖世英雄
A peerless and invincible hero,

331
00:29:58,950 --> 00:30:02,340
横扫千军的勇将猛帅
a bold and resourceful general capable of defeating vast armies.

332
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:07,890
可老天却偏偏不成全他
But fate wasn't on his side.

333
00:30:09,950 --> 00:30:13,660
在垓下 中了汉军的十面埋伏
At Gaixia he fell into an ambush set by the Han king,

334
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:16,680
让刘邦给困死了
Liu Bang.

335
00:30:17,760 --> 00:30:20,450
那天晚上 刮着大风
A great wind blew up on that night.

336
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:24,970
刘邦的兵 唱了一宿的楚歌
Liu Bang's troops sang the songs of the kingdom of Chu all night long.

337
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:28,820
楚国的人马 以为刘邦得了楚地
The Chu warriors assumed Liu Bang already occupied their homeland.

338
00:30:28,890 --> 00:30:32,090
全都慌了神了 跑光了
In a great panic, they fled.

339
00:30:32,450 --> 00:30:35,050
听得霸王 也掉下泪来
Even the king was weeping.

340
00:30:37,820 --> 00:30:40,240
人纵有万般能耐
No matter how resourceful you are,

341
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:44,360
可终也敌不过天命
you can't fight fate.

342
00:30:45,940 --> 00:30:48,140
那霸王风云一世
The king had once been all-powerful,

343
00:30:48,420 --> 00:30:49,540
临到头
but in the end,

344
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:53,920
就剩下了 一匹马和一个女人 还跟着他
all he had left was one woman and one horse.

345
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:58,630
霸王让乌骓马逃命 乌骓马不去
He tried to get his steed to run away, but it wouldn't go.

346
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:02,160
让虞姬走人 虞姬不肯
He wanted his concubine to flee, but she stayed too.

347
00:31:02,880 --> 00:31:06,550
那虞姬 最后一次为霸王斟酒
For the very last time, Concubine Yu poured wine for her king

348
00:31:06,950 --> 00:31:09,940
最后一回 为霸王舞剑
and danced for him with a sword,

349
00:31:10,150 --> 00:31:16,160
尔后 拔剑自刎 从一而终啊
then cut her throat with it, faithful to the king unto death.

350
00:31:20,100 --> 00:31:21,450
讲这出戏
There's a lesson...

351
00:31:22,700 --> 00:31:26,260
是这里边 有个唱戏和做人的道理
...in this story for all of us

352
00:31:27,280 --> 00:31:31,320
人 得自个儿成全自个儿
that each person is responsible for his or her own fate.

353
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:47,920
“力拔山兮” 
I am so strong I can uproot the mountains,

354
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:53,840
“气盖世”
My courage is renowned.

355
00:31:54,200 --> 00:32:01,900
“时不利兮”
I've fallen on bad times,

356
00:32:02,300 --> 00:32:06,780
“骓不逝”
Yet even my horse won't run away to save itself

357
00:32:15,990 --> 00:32:18,920
张宅上 把订戏的差 委了您…
Old Man Zhang has commissioned you to hire an opera troupe.

358
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:21,990
那您就是 我们喜福成的衣食父母
You're like a fairy godmother to us.

359
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:23,810
啊 您抬举抬举呢
With your patronage,

360
00:32:23,950 --> 00:32:26,370
孩子们年下 就穿上新衣裳了
the children will have new clothes to wear in the New Year.

361
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:31,210
衣裳的事 好穿
New clothes are not a problem.

362
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:32,960
戏活难做
The opera, however, is no simple matter.

363
00:32:33,040 --> 00:32:33,670
诶 对啊
Yes.

364
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:35,180
张公公 那是当年
When he was a palace eunuch, Old Man Zhang...

365
00:32:35,180 --> 00:32:37,450
陪太后老佛爷 听过戏的主儿
...attended operas with the Empress Dowager herself.

366
00:32:37,450 --> 00:32:38,400
那是 那是
That's it.

367
00:32:38,780 --> 00:32:39,860
糊弄得了吗
So you can't put anything over on him.

368
00:32:40,320 --> 00:32:41,040
敢吗
Not that anyone would try!

369
00:32:43,250 --> 00:32:45,700
玩艺儿要是不灵 新衣裳…
You realise that if this little number doesn't make the grade,

370
00:32:46,660 --> 00:32:48,000
砸了我的脸面 没什么
I could lose a lot of face, but that's nothing.

371
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,670
- 像您这样的 - 啊
- He could... - Me?

372
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:51,570
能把您给囚起来
He could have you locked up!

373
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,390
- 这孩子 有点意思啊 - 啊
- This kid's got something. - What?

