You've stuffed it up!

394
00:34:26,070 --> 00:34:27,160
叫你错
You've stuffed it up!

395
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:32,280
叫你错 我叫你错 我叫你错 错呀你 错…
You've stuffed it up! Stuffed it up!

