“奴把袈裟扯破”
And I rend my Buddhist gown!

406
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:56,420
“自从我...”
For year upon year,

407
00:35:56,680 --> 00:36:00,930
“随大王…”
all over the land, I've followed my king...

408
00:36:02,740 --> 00:36:13,560
“东征西战…”
...on his military campaigns

409
00:36:24,250 --> 00:36:35,540
“受风霜与劳碌 年复年年…”
