It stings when the sweat gets into a scratch over my eye.

434
00:38:41,740 --> 00:38:43,780
俩孩子 一块儿去吧
Aren't the two kids going in together?

435
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:46,850
老规矩了
No.

436
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:49,550
- 多少年的老规矩了 - 诶
