00:39:58,220 --> 00:40:01,540
是大清宣统 二十四年
It's the 24th year of Emperor Xuantong's rein.

450
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:06,140
你 过来
Come over here.

451
00:40:07,640 --> 00:40:08,630
我…我
I...

452
00:40:09,200 --> 00:40:10,430
我找我师哥
I want Shitou.

453
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:12,990
