You won't harm anything.

457
00:41:10,570 --> 00:41:11,360
来
Come over.

458
00:41:12,500 --> 00:41:13,790
诶...来呀
Come to me!

459
00:41:50,210 --> 00:41:50,940
豆子
Douzi!

460
00:41:56,330 --> 00:41:57,230
关老板
Master Guan.

461
00:41:57,710 --> 00:42:00,760
- 张公公 让我谢谢您 - 你怎么了 说话呀
- Mr. Zhang asked me to thank you. - What's happened to you? Say something!

462
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:03,460
哑巴啦
Have you gone dumb?

463
00:42:04,660 --> 00:42:05,700
说话呀
Speak to me!

464
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,720
小豆子
Douzi,

