Oppose Japan's invasion of North China!

475
00:44:04,450 --> 00:44:06,510
糟了糟了 又是那些学生
Damn! It's those students again.

476
00:44:21,080 --> 00:44:24,320
“保卫华北 打倒日本帝国主义”
Down with Japanese imperialism! Death is preferable to enslavement!

477
00:44:24,530 --> 00:44:26,810
喂 这不是照片上那俩戏子吗
Aren't those the two actors in the photograph?

478
00:44:29,480 --> 00:44:31,610
眼瞅就要当亡国奴了 你知道吗
Don't you know you're playing into the hands of the Japanese?

479
00:44:32,120 --> 00:44:33,760
妖里妖气的 你唱什么戏
Yeah, how can you tart yourself up and sing opera at a time like this?

480
00:44:33,880 --> 00:44:36,100
没家没国的 你们有没有中国人的良心
Don't you have the least bit of feeling for your country?

481
