00:45:13,010 --> 00:45:14,850
敢情欺负的还是中国人呀
Instead, they pick on fellow Chinese!

493
00:45:14,940 --> 00:45:18,570
瞎哄呗 学生们不都没娶过媳妇吗
They're just looking for trouble. None of them have married yet,

494
00:45:19,080 --> 00:45:21,310
火气壮 又没钱找姑娘
and they've got no money to get any girls,

495
00:45:21,580 --> 00:45:24,510
