蝶衣
Dieyi,

505
00:45:47,240 --> 00:45:48,820
那儿现成了棺材铺了
Zhang's home is now a coffin shop!

506
00:45:49,290 --> 00:45:50,490
我昨儿刚去的
I went there just yesterday.

507
00:45:51,100 --> 00:45:53,120
又去找那把剑去了 是不
You were looking for that sword, weren't you?

508
00:45:53,460 --> 00:45:54,720
早不知卖哪儿去了
It was probably sold off years ago.

509
00:46:02,910 --> 00:46:06,010
程蝶衣…程蝶衣…
Cheng Dieyi! Cheng Dieyi!

