00:46:58,310 --> 00:46:59,030
段老板
Mr Duan...

520
00:47:00,830 --> 00:47:02,020
急急风催半天了
The orchestra's been warming up for ages.

521
00:47:02,180 --> 00:47:03,430
您再紧把手
Please hurry!

522
00:47:04,320 --> 00:47:05,410
知道了 知道了
I know. I know.

523
00:47:06,520 --> 00:47:07,750
我先亮一嗓子
Let me first practise a few scales.

524
00:47:08,660 --> 00:47:11,010
让他们知道 票没白买 不就得了
That way they'll know they'll be getting their money's worth.

