bestowed such a gift upon her favourite actors.

562
00:50:52,110 --> 00:50:52,910
有吗
If so,

563
00:50:53,630 --> 00:50:54,670
没有吧
I'd never heard of it!

564
00:50:59,060 --> 00:50:59,820
四爷
Master Yuan,

565
00:51:00,600 --> 00:51:02,800
您这让我们蝶衣 怎么当得起啊
how can our Dieyi be worthy of your favour?

566
00:51:07,240 --> 00:51:09,140
“霸王别姬”这一折
"Farewell My Concubine"...

567
00:51:09,790 --> 00:51:11,140
渊源已久
...has a long history.

568
00:51:12,020 --> 00:51:14,060
本是从昆剧老本
It evolved from...

569
00:51:14,450 --> 00:51:17,040
“千金记”里脱胎出来的
...the old-style opera "The Gold Strategy".

570
00:51:17,880 --> 00:51:21,040
好多名家 都在这出上唱栽过
Many famous actors have fallen down in this role.

571
00:51:22,760 --> 00:51:24,840
独你程老板的虞姬
Your evocation of the Concubine Yu...

572
00:51:25,640 --> 00:51:27,960
快入纯青之境
...lifts it into a higher realm.

573
00:51:34,130 --> 00:51:35,380
有点意思
Impressive.

574
00:51:42,570 --> 00:51:44,440
有那么一二刻
For a moment or two,

575
00:51:46,260 --> 00:51:48,440
袁某也恍惚起来
this Yuan fellow was so entranced

576
00:51:50,370 --> 00:51:53,460
疑为虞姬 转世再现啦
he believed Concubine Yu had actually come back to life!

577
00:51:59,530 --> 00:52:00,380
段老板…
Mr Duan...

578
00:52:01,400 --> 00:52:03,290
霸王回营亮相
when the king returns to camp...

579
00:52:03,770 --> 00:52:05,500
到和虞姬相见
...and meets Concubine Yu,

580
00:52:06,900 --> 00:52:08,300
按老规矩…
custom has it...

581
00:52:08,480 --> 00:52:09,340
是 四爷
Yes, Master Yuan.

582
00:52:12,500 --> 00:52:16,670
按老规矩是定然七步 你只走了五步
Custom has it he takes seven steps. Yet you take but five.

583
00:52:17,970 --> 00:52:20,210
楚霸王 气度尊贵
If the King of Chu fails to bear himself with majestic dignity,

584
00:52:21,180 --> 00:52:22,670
要是威而不重
he's little better than...

585
00:52:23,290 --> 00:52:25,900
不成了江湖上的黄天霸了
...a gangster putting on airs!

586
00:52:27,120 --> 00:52:27,800
四爷
Master Yuan,

587
00:52:28,420 --> 00:52:29,810
您梨园大拿呀
you are a master of the theatre arts.

588
00:52:30,600 --> 00:52:33,400
文武昆乱不挡 六场通透
You are expert in all the varieties and facets of opera.

589
00:52:33,970 --> 00:52:35,130
您能有错吗
Could we doubt your word?

590
00:52:36,270 --> 00:52:38,300
- 哦 - 您要是都出了错
- Yes. - Indeed,

591
00:52:38,930 --> 00:52:40,840
那我们兄弟 这点玩艺儿…
we are presumptuous to parade our meagre talents...

592
00:52:41,310 --> 00:52:42,810
还敢在北平的戏园子里露吗
in the theatres of Peiping.

593
00:52:42,810 --> 00:52:44,910
四爷 您得栽培我们
Please give us the benefit of your advice and criticism.

594
00:52:48,170 --> 00:52:49,550
如不嫌弃
If it's not beneath you,

595
00:52:50,210 --> 00:52:53,690
请二位到舍下 小酌几杯 然后细谈
 I'd like to invite you to my humble home for some wine.

596
00:52:54,700 --> 00:52:55,790
实话说
There is...

597
00:52:56,530 --> 00:52:59,370
这出戏的学问 还真是不浅
There is so much still to be said about this opera.

598
00:52:59,490 --> 00:53:00,410
哟 四爷
Master Yuan,

599
00:53:01,410 --> 00:53:02,360
对您不住
I'm terribly sorry.

600
00:53:02,900 --> 00:53:03,840
赶巧了
Sorry!

601
00:53:04,450 --> 00:53:05,260
我得…
I've another...

602
00:53:07,250 --> 00:53:09,320
喝一壶花酒去
...drinking engagement with a courtesan.

603
00:53:16,500 --> 00:53:18,030
另有雅趣
You have other refined entertainments planned!

604
00:53:19,660 --> 00:53:20,380
好
Excellent!

605
00:53:22,000 --> 00:53:23,160
程老板呢
And Mr Cheng?

606
00:53:23,950 --> 00:53:24,620
我...
Me...

607
00:53:31,280 --> 00:53:33,640
那么日后踏雪访梅
Then we shall exchange poetic thoughts...

608
00:53:34,160 --> 00:53:35,740
再谈不迟
...some other day.

609
00:53:37,460 --> 00:53:38,500
失陪了
I'll take my leave.

610
00:53:40,250 --> 00:53:41,560
四爷 您慢走
Take care, Master Yuan.

611
00:53:48,160 --> 00:53:49,460
- 蝶衣 - 诶
- Dieyi, - What?

612
00:53:50,050 --> 00:53:50,960
我也走了
Dieyi, I'm off as well.

613
00:53:56,530 --> 00:53:59,540
彩凤 金燕 丽君 淑瑷 秋香
Caifeng, Jinyan, Lijun, Shuyuan, Qiuxiang...

614
00:53:59,660 --> 00:54:00,940
接客了
come entertain our guest.

615
00:54:02,480 --> 00:54:04,670
哟 段老板 您来啦
Mr Duan, this way please.

616
00:54:04,780 --> 00:54:05,490
段老板
Mr Duan,

617
00:54:05,600 --> 00:54:08,620
段老板 您有些日子没来了 太久了...
We haven't seen you for a while, Mr Duan.

618
00:54:08,620 --> 00:54:10,480
这心里还怪惦记的
We've missed you.

619
00:54:12,020 --> 00:54:13,530
会会菊仙姑娘
I'd like to see Miss Juxian.

620
00:54:13,640 --> 00:54:16,030
哟 这话怎么说的呢
Ah, how shall I put it?

621
00:54:16,190 --> 00:54:17,050
您倒早…
You should...

622
00:54:17,730 --> 00:54:19,670
您倒早言语呀
You should have said something earlier.

623
00:54:20,850 --> 00:54:22,850
菊仙姑娘 这阵子不在
She's not here at the moment.

624
00:54:23,210 --> 00:54:25,700
她出条子 应饭局子去了
She was asked out to dinner.

625
00:54:25,960 --> 00:54:28,620
这可怎么好啊 要不这么着吧
What to do? How about this...

626
00:54:29,150 --> 00:54:31,010
姐给你找个好的 啊
We'll find you a good substitute.

627
00:54:31,730 --> 00:54:32,500
彩凤
Caifeng,

628
00:54:32,810 --> 00:54:34,900
- 诶 - 你来陪陪段老板
- What? - come keep Mr Duan company!

629
00:54:36,250 --> 00:54:38,730
小楼 我就不陪你了
I'll take my leave.

630
00:54:51,690 --> 00:54:53,410
给哥哥透个实情
Tell me the truth.

631
00:54:55,250 --> 00:54:57,560
菊仙姑娘 在哪间屋啊
Where is Juxian really?

632
00:54:59,810 --> 00:55:03,940
是在底下呀 还是在上头
Upstairs or... down?

633
00:55:05,250 --> 00:55:08,590
凤凰当然栖高枝啦
The phoenix roosts on the highest branches of course!

634
00:55:10,500 --> 00:55:12,500
可人家是头牌
But she's pretty high class.

635
00:55:13,910 --> 00:55:15,500
你够得着吗
You reckon she'll go for you?

636
00:55:20,500 --> 00:55:21,810
让你说着了
You said it!

637
00:55:22,810 --> 00:55:25,320
哥哥我就是 专傍头牌的
I specialise in high class.

638
00:55:29,620 --> 00:55:31,170
哎呀 菊仙姑娘…
Oh, Miss Juxian...

639
00:55:31,420 --> 00:55:32,290
你王八蛋
Bastards!

640
00:55:32,620 --> 00:55:34,530
王八蛋就王八蛋
OK, we're bastards!

641
00:55:34,530 --> 00:55:35,310
去呀
Go for it then.

642
00:55:35,920 --> 00:55:37,620
- 你不是要傍头牌吗 - 嗯
- What are you waiting for? - Yes.

643
00:55:38,030 --> 00:55:40,140
看这几位爷 不把你剁了当菜吃
Let's see if those guys don't just make mincemeat of you!

644
00:55:45,120 --> 00:55:46,720
我告诉你 我真急了
I'm really angry now!

645
00:55:46,720 --> 00:55:49,620
咹 这...急...急了 好呀
We like it when you're angry!

646
00:55:50,760 --> 00:55:51,620
再闹
Cut it out...

647
00:55:53,190 --> 00:55:54,160
再闹我跳了
or I'll jump!

648
00:55:54,460 --> 00:55:56,200
跳呀 你跳呀
Jump!

649
00:55:56,990 --> 00:55:59,460
你前脚跳 我后脚跳
I'll follow on your heels.

650
00:55:59,920 --> 00:56:04,180
宁在花下死 做鬼也风流
Such a death would be ecstasy. I'd be a merry ghost.

651
00:56:04,880 --> 00:56:06,340
我们就跟你死
If you die, we'll all die,

652
00:56:06,960 --> 00:56:08,370
做你棺材板
and be the planks in your coffin.

653
00:56:13,270 --> 00:56:13,980
小楼
Xiaolou!

654
00:56:29,820 --> 00:56:31,060
这帮小子坏透了
These guys are revolting!

655
00:56:31,600 --> 00:56:34,120
他们逼着我 嘴对嘴地喂他们酒喝
They were forcing me to drink wine from their mouths.

656
00:56:36,360 --> 00:56:40,300
怎么着 王八蛋 你们跳呀
Come on, assholes. Jump!

657
00:56:40,470 --> 00:56:41,860
姑奶奶跳了 怎么着
This lady's done it. Now's your turn!

658
00:56:42,330 --> 00:56:43,520
王八蛋
Bastards!

659
00:56:44,440 --> 00:56:45,860
都是她妈丫头养的
Pack of fucking sissies!

660
00:56:47,540 --> 00:56:52,590
下去就他妈下去 下去 走
All right, if we have to go down, let's go!

661
00:57:08,410 --> 00:57:10,440
是段老板呐
Oh, it's Mr Duan!

662
00:57:11,490 --> 00:57:12,440
段老板
Listen,

663
00:57:13,320 --> 00:57:15,970
咱们到这儿来 可都是来找乐子的
we're all here to have a good time,

664
00:57:16,410 --> 00:57:20,920
扔出去的 可都是白花花响当当的大洋啊
and we're all spending good money.

665
00:57:22,690 --> 00:57:23,460
今儿个
So...

666
00:57:23,610 --> 00:57:25,310
谁跟谁 都别找不痛快
...let's not pick fights with each other.

667
00:57:29,240 --> 00:57:30,100
别找不痛快
Don't look for trouble.

668
00:57:30,180 --> 00:57:31,910
走吧 走吧
Get out of here.

669
00:57:32,000 --> 00:57:32,610
松手
Let go.

670
00:57:32,710 --> 00:57:34,690
- 喂 别介呀… - 别介
- Don't get upset. - - Don't get upset?

671
00:57:35,520 --> 00:57:36,460
怂啦
Scared?

672
00:57:44,180 --> 00:57:45,020
菊仙
Juxian,

673
00:57:45,760 --> 00:57:47,550
这可就是你的不周到了
this is all really your fault.

674
00:57:48,930 --> 00:57:51,790
你怎么没告诉各位爷 今儿是什么日子
Didn't you tell these gentlemen today's a special day?

675
00:58:08,800 --> 00:58:11,520
今儿个 不是咱俩定亲的喜日子吗
That we decided to announce our engagement today?

676
00:58:19,940 --> 00:58:20,700
对
That's right!

677
00:58:22,150 --> 00:58:25,460
今儿个 是姑奶奶定亲的喜日子
Today is this lady's happy day.

678
00:58:27,390 --> 00:58:28,120
怎么着
So?

679
00:58:28,900 --> 00:58:30,420
给姑奶奶贺喜吧
Aren't you going to offer your congratulations?

680
00:58:31,460 --> 00:58:34,580
给姑奶奶敬酒吧
Drink a toast to me!

681
00:59:25,020 --> 00:59:28,010
爷们儿 哄他妈谁呢
Who the fuck are they kidding?

682
00:59:28,980 --> 00:59:30,520
- 哟 各位爷 - 你笨
- Gentlemen, - You're stupid.

683
00:59:30,820 --> 00:59:32,440
今儿是我大喜的日子
on this, my happiest day...

684
00:59:32,570 --> 00:59:33,130
滚开
Get ou!

685
00:59:33,130 --> 00:59:34,440
我得敬敬各位爷
allow me to drink to all of you!

686
00:59:36,820 --> 00:59:38,160
给各位爷 醒醒酒
And now something to sober you up.

687
00:59:40,990 --> 00:59:42,010
给我叫一好
Wish us well!

688
00:59:42,190 --> 00:59:43,590
诶 小楼
Xiaolou,

689
01:00:01,360 --> 01:00:05,480
听说 您在八大胡同打出名来了
I heard you got into a fight at the House of Blossoms.

690
01:00:05,980 --> 01:00:07,850
唵 啊
What?

691
01:00:08,380 --> 01:00:10,320
这武二郎 碰上西门庆了
You know the old story about Pan Jinlian's husband

692
01:00:10,620 --> 01:00:11,310
不打
meeting the man who screwed her?

693
01:00:11,620 --> 01:00:12,720
不打 能成吗
Did he have any choice but to fight?

694
01:00:14,060 --> 01:00:16,940
这么说 有个潘金莲啦
Does this mean there's a Pan Jinlian in your life?

695
01:00:17,320 --> 01:00:18,280
这是什么话
What are you saying?

696
01:00:18,280 --> 01:00:19,730
你想听什么话
What do you want to hear?

697
01:00:19,900 --> 01:00:20,760
嗨
Hi.

698
01:00:21,600 --> 01:00:23,710
不过是救人解难 玩玩呗
I was just fooling around. "Damsel in distress"...

699
01:00:24,190 --> 01:00:25,080
又不当真
and all that - no big deal.

700
01:00:26,580 --> 01:00:27,280
蝶衣
Dieyi, 

701
01:00:28,140 --> 01:00:30,010
什么时候 一块儿去逛逛
Come there with me sometime.

702
01:00:30,620 --> 01:00:31,940
就知道了
You'll see what it's like.

703
01:00:33,650 --> 01:00:34,940
嘿呦
Hey, yo.

704
01:00:45,750 --> 01:00:46,430
兄弟
Bro.

705
01:00:47,550 --> 01:00:48,170
哟
Hey.

706
01:00:49,130 --> 01:00:50,140
对不住 兄弟
I'm sorry. I really am!

707
01:00:51,900 --> 01:00:53,430
师哥今儿 神不在家
I just wasn't thinking.

708
01:00:53,890 --> 01:00:54,990
自己是...是
I really...

709
01:00:55,130 --> 01:00:56,070
说走嘴了
...put my foot in it this time.

710
01:00:58,160 --> 01:00:59,190
师哥该死
I'm a damn fool.

711
01:01:03,790 --> 01:01:04,690
你忘了
Have you forgotten...

712
01:01:05,650 --> 01:01:07,150
咱们是怎么唱红的
...the secret of our success?

713
01:01:09,820 --> 01:01:11,680
还不就凭了师傅一句话
Don't you remember our teacher's words?

714
01:01:15,170 --> 01:01:16,050
什么话呀
Which words were they?

715
01:01:18,110 --> 01:01:19,230
从一而终
Stick together till the day you die.

716
01:01:21,340 --> 01:01:22,070
师哥
Bro.

717
01:01:23,060 --> 01:01:24,100
我要让你跟我...
I want you to be with me...

718
01:01:25,350 --> 01:01:26,010
不对...
I mean...

719
01:01:26,880 --> 01:01:28,850
就让我跟你 好好唱一辈子戏
I want to be with you the rest of my life.

720
01:01:29,130 --> 01:01:30,020
不行吗
Can't we?

721
01:01:32,140 --> 01:01:32,820
这不…
We've...

722
01:01:33,220 --> 01:01:35,120
这不 小半辈子都唱过来了吗
We've come this far together, haven't we?

723
01:01:35,120 --> 01:01:35,910
不行
It's not enough.

724
01:01:36,480 --> 01:01:37,570
说的是一辈子
I'm talking about a lifetime.

725
01:01:37,950 --> 01:01:40,530
差一年 一个月 一天 一个时辰
One year, one month, one day, even one second less

726
01:01:40,890 --> 01:01:42,000
都不算一辈子
makes it less than a lifetime!

727
01:01:50,370 --> 01:01:51,120
蝶衣
Dieyi,

728
01:01:51,730 --> 01:01:54,420
你可真是 不疯魔 不成活呀
Dieyi, you really are obsessed.

729
01:01:55,690 --> 01:01:57,850
唱戏得疯魔 不假
You're obsessed on stage...

730
01:01:58,790 --> 01:02:00,480
可要是活着 也疯魔
and it carries over into your life.

731
01:02:01,650 --> 01:02:05,140
在这人世上 在这凡人堆里
But how are we going to get through the days and make it

732
01:02:06,640 --> 01:02:08,470
咱们可怎么活哟
in the real world, among ordinary people?

733
01:02:10,860 --> 01:02:13,240
来 给师哥勾个脸
Give me a hand with my makeup, will you?

734
01:02:40,060 --> 01:02:40,930
“妃子”
Oh my concubine!

735
01:02:43,290 --> 01:02:45,620
“四面俱是楚国歌声”
The songs of Chu can be heard on all sides!

736
01:02:45,830 --> 01:02:52,100
“定是刘邦得了楚地 孤大势去矣”
Liu Bang has surely taken my kingdom! I'm finished!

737
01:02:53,660 --> 01:02:54,560
“啊 大王”
My king!

738
01:02:54,560 --> 01:02:56,160
“依孤看来”
I fear...

739
01:02:56,400 --> 01:03:11,280
“今日是你我分别之日了”
...that today is the day we must part

740
01:03:55,610 --> 01:03:57,710
真他妈想当太太奶奶啦 你
So you want to become a fucking hoity-toity rich man's wife!

741
01:04:01,610 --> 01:04:03,320
做你娘的玻璃梦 去吧
Go live out this goddamn fantasy then.

742
01:04:03,700 --> 01:04:05,660
你当出了这门儿 把脸一抹洒
But you're kidding yourself if you think that when you walk out this door,

743
01:04:05,740 --> 01:04:07,260
你还真成了良人啦
you'll become a lady of virtue!

744
01:04:07,690 --> 01:04:09,370
你当这世上的狼啊虎啊
You think the wolves and tigers...

745
01:04:09,470 --> 01:04:10,830
就都不认得你啦
...won't recognise your scent anymore?

746
01:04:12,760 --> 01:04:13,820
哟
Hey,

747
01:04:14,300 --> 01:04:15,910
可吓死我啦
How you frighten me!

748
01:04:18,200 --> 01:04:19,280
我告诉你
Let me tell you something.

749
01:04:20,670 --> 01:04:23,250
那窑姐儿 永远是窑姐儿
Once a whore, always a whore.

750
01:04:25,100 --> 01:04:26,660
你记住我这话
Just remember that.

751
01:04:29,760 --> 01:04:31,280
这就是你的命
This is your fate!

752
01:04:36,810 --> 01:04:37,520
成
Fine.

753
01:04:38,160 --> 01:04:39,360
回见了您呐
See you around.

754
01:04:48,780 --> 01:04:51,850
袁四爷送条幅
Master Yuan has presented you with a pennant.

755
01:04:53,000 --> 01:04:56,240
“风华绝代”
It reads, "The beauty of the age".

756
01:04:56,560 --> 01:05:09,100
程蝶衣 程老板
Dieyi Cheng, Mr Cheng!

757
01:05:18,730 --> 01:05:28,800
程蝶衣 程老板
Dieyi Cheng, Mr Cheng!

758
01:05:47,160 --> 01:05:47,940
咦哟
Eh, yo.

759
01:05:48,860 --> 01:05:50,360
你怎么上这儿来了
What are you doing here?

760
01:05:54,060 --> 01:05:55,530
又怎么了 菊仙
What is it, Juxian?

761
01:05:56,050 --> 01:05:57,210
来 来 来 进来
Come on in!

762
01:05:57,610 --> 01:05:58,340
进来说
Come on in!

763
01:05:58,870 --> 01:05:59,740
你出来
No, you come out!

764
01:06:03,910 --> 01:06:07,160
对诶 怎么光着脚啊 这么凉的天
What are you doing barefoot on such a cold day?

765
01:06:10,860 --> 01:06:11,800
出了什么事啦
What's happened?

766
01:06:13,200 --> 01:06:14,250
赶出来了
I was kicked out.

767
01:06:15,210 --> 01:06:17,280
花满楼 不留许过婚的人
The House of Blossoms won't keep an engaged woman.

768
01:06:23,610 --> 01:06:24,910
程老板 程老板
Mr Cheng,

769
01:06:34,550 --> 01:06:35,670
来...来
Come.

770
01:06:36,180 --> 01:06:38,530
来 过来 过来见见
Come. Let me introduce you.

771
01:06:39,690 --> 01:06:41,420
这是 菊仙小姐
This is Miss Juxian.

772
01:06:42,510 --> 01:06:43,730
这就是我的亲师弟
This is my stage brother.

773
01:06:44,330 --> 01:06:46,090
你瞧见了 演虞姬的
You've seen him as Concubine Yu.

774
01:06:47,260 --> 01:06:47,960
哟
Hey,

775
01:06:48,500 --> 01:06:50,020
常听小楼念叨您
Xiaolou speaks of you so often,

776
01:06:50,640 --> 01:06:52,110
听都听成熟人了
I feel like we're old friends.

777
01:06:53,920 --> 01:06:57,520
噢 菊仙小姐 失陪了
Ah, Miss Juxian. I must be going.

778
01:07:08,210 --> 01:07:09,080
小楼
Xiaolou,

779
01:07:11,030 --> 01:07:12,430
那天在花满楼
that day at the House of Blossoms...

780
01:07:13,080 --> 01:07:14,830
要不是 你在楼底下接着
If you hadn't caught me,

781
01:07:16,160 --> 01:07:17,600
我早就入土了
I'd be six feet under by now.

782
01:07:22,610 --> 01:07:26,490
那杯定亲酒 可是你先喝了一半
Remember, it was you who proposed to me.

783
01:07:27,540 --> 01:07:28,580
菊仙命苦
I'm used to hardship.

784
01:07:30,240 --> 01:07:31,420
你要是收留她
If you take me in...

785
01:07:32,290 --> 01:07:33,900
有人当牛做马 侍侯你
I'll wait on you hand and foot.

786
01:07:36,190 --> 01:07:37,260
你要是嫌弃她
If you tire of me,

787
01:07:39,520 --> 01:07:42,000
大不了 她再跳回楼
I'll jump again and kill myself. No big deal, really.

788
01:07:57,200 --> 01:07:58,940
这妞可够厉害的
What a dragon lady!

789
01:08:01,260 --> 01:08:03,430
服 我服 啊
Incredible!

790
01:08:03,720 --> 01:08:05,880
这他妈就是一本大戏呀
This is a major production.

791
01:08:08,490 --> 01:08:11,960
什么时候 洞房花烛夜呀
When's the performance of "Candlelit Night in the Bridal Chamber"?

792
01:08:14,590 --> 01:08:15,450
今儿晚上
Tonight.

793
01:08:15,450 --> 01:08:16,400
好 好
Great!

794
01:08:16,510 --> 01:08:17,390
还有哪
Hold on.

795
01:08:18,880 --> 01:08:22,140
你呀 得当着戏班子 老少爷们的面儿
I want a formal betrothal ceremony...

796
01:08:22,710 --> 01:08:24,100
先给我办定亲礼
...to which the entire company is invited.

797
01:08:25,270 --> 01:08:27,380
我得堂堂正正地 进你段家的门
I want to enter your home as a proper bride.

798
01:08:28,960 --> 01:08:30,600
嫌我偷工减料啊
You don't think I plan to cut corners, do you?

799
01:08:31,780 --> 01:08:35,010
那成 今儿晚上就是定亲礼
The formal engagement ceremony will be tonight.

800
01:08:35,400 --> 01:08:36,760
我请各位赏光
Gentlemen, we request the pleasure of your company.

801
01:08:43,610 --> 01:08:44,920
菊仙小姐
Miss Juxian...

802
01:08:46,520 --> 01:08:48,480
您挨哪儿 学的戏啊
where did you study opera?

803
01:08:50,010 --> 01:08:50,640
哟
Oh.

804
01:08:50,840 --> 01:08:52,300
我哪儿学过戏呀
Me, study opera? What makes you think I studied opera?

805
01:08:54,480 --> 01:08:57,760
没学过呀 那就别洒狗血了
Just the way you're overplaying your part.

806
01:09:02,760 --> 01:09:03,480
蝶衣
Dieyi,

807
01:09:03,890 --> 01:09:04,980
叫声嫂子吧
she's like your sister-in-law now.

808
01:09:05,580 --> 01:09:06,450
不叫不成了
Call her that.

809
01:09:07,480 --> 01:09:09,330
还有今儿晚上 证婚人这活儿
Also, at the engagement party tonight...

810
01:09:10,060 --> 01:09:11,060
你得给我接下来
I'd like you to be best man.

811
01:09:14,990 --> 01:09:18,320
黄天霸和妓女的戏 不会演
I haven't learnt the opera "Gangster King and his Whore".

812
01:09:20,620 --> 01:09:22,030
师傅没教过
Our teacher never taught us that one.

813
01:09:22,290 --> 01:09:24,400
这...这是哪儿和哪儿呢
What are you on about?

814
01:09:24,740 --> 01:09:25,600
师弟
Dieyi,

815
01:09:26,360 --> 01:09:28,600
小楼在人前人后提起您来
Xiaolou has never said an ill word about you

816
01:09:28,850 --> 01:09:31,150
说的 可都是厚道话儿
in public or private.

817
01:09:36,040 --> 01:09:36,800
别走
Don't leave!

818
01:09:41,300 --> 01:09:42,340
你上哪儿去
Where are you going?

819
01:09:44,650 --> 01:09:47,940
我上哪儿去 你管得着吗
None of your business.

820
01:09:49,600 --> 01:09:50,900
- 诶 小... - 师哥
- Hey, Xiao... - Xiaolou!

821
01:09:53,330 --> 01:09:54,610
师哥 你别走
Please don't go!

822
01:09:56,190 --> 01:09:59,260
袁四爷今儿晚上 请咱们过去
Master Yuan wants us to visit him tonight.

823
01:10:00,500 --> 01:10:01,680
要栽培咱们
He wants to become our patron.

824
01:10:02,520 --> 01:10:05,120
姓袁的 他管得着姓段的吗
Who does he think he is? No one tells me what to do.

825
01:10:07,630 --> 01:10:11,020
我是假霸王 你是真虞姬
I'm just a fake king. You really are Concubine Yu.

826
01:10:11,810 --> 01:10:13,390
让他栽培你一个人去吧
Let him patronise you if you like.

827
01:10:13,900 --> 01:10:14,680
师哥
Xiaolou!

828
01:10:15,610 --> 01:10:16,490
师哥
Xiaolou!

829
01:10:41,280 --> 01:10:44,640
这对翎子 难得
A headdress of this quality is a rare thing.

830
01:10:47,080 --> 01:10:52,090
是从活雉鸡的尾巴上 生生收取的
Only if plucked from the tail of a live pheasant

831
01:10:54,240 --> 01:10:55,710
这才够柔软
are the feathers so soft,

832
01:10:57,240 --> 01:10:58,280
够伶俐
lithe...

833
01:10:59,800 --> 01:11:00,980
够漂亮
...and beautiful.

834
01:11:02,610 --> 01:11:04,300
我恭候大驾啦
I respectfully await your good self!

835
01:11:43,440 --> 01:11:44,690
尘世中
In this world,

836
01:11:45,420 --> 01:11:49,140
男子阳污 女子阴秽
there is foulness in both men and women.

837
01:11:50,250 --> 01:11:54,220
独观世音 集两者之精 于一身
Only the Bodhisattva embodies both male and female essences.

838
01:11:57,980 --> 01:12:00,110
欢喜无量啊
Such ecstasy!

839
01:12:16,530 --> 01:12:18,640
这把剑 有些来历
This sword has a history.

840
01:12:19,610 --> 01:12:22,240
是大太监张某的旧物
It once belonged to the eunuch Zhang.

841
01:12:23,240 --> 01:12:24,720
张家破败时
When Zhang went bankrupt,

842
01:12:25,010 --> 01:12:27,780
是费了大周折 弄到手的
I went to great trouble to acquire it.

843
01:12:29,550 --> 01:12:31,150
如此看来…
I can see from this

844
01:12:32,260 --> 01:12:35,330
此物是你的旧相识了
you're old acquaintances.

845
01:12:37,480 --> 01:12:39,380
果然世上的事
Amazing, one searches far and wide for something...

846
01:12:39,970 --> 01:12:43,240
是踏破铁鞋无觅处啊
...only to stumble upon it by chance.

847
01:12:51,480 --> 01:12:52,380
喜欢
Like it?

848
01:12:54,040 --> 01:12:54,770
我…
I...

849
01:12:56,050 --> 01:13:00,720
你我之间不言钱 那个字眼实在不雅
Let's not have any vulgar talk of money between us.

850
01:13:03,450 --> 01:13:06,320
自古宝剑酬知已
A precious sword is the classic gift for one's most intimate friend.

851
01:13:09,140 --> 01:13:10,030
程老板
Mr Cheng,

852
01:13:11,740 --> 01:13:14,670
愿做我的红尘知己吗
Mr Cheng, will you be my most intimate friend?

853
01:13:15,680 --> 01:13:24,900
“汉兵已略地”
The soldiers of Han have invaded

854
01:13:25,620 --> 01:13:34,840
“四面楚歌声”
The songs of Chu can be heard on all sides

855
01:13:34,960 --> 01:13:35,670
不
No.

856
01:13:36,580 --> 01:13:37,280
不
No.

857
01:13:38,580 --> 01:13:47,480
“君王意气尽”
Since the good king has lost his fighting spirit

858
01:13:49,430 --> 01:14:01,550
“贱妾何聊生”
Why should his humble concubine value her life?

859
01:14:05,600 --> 01:14:06,290
别动
Don't!

860
01:14:07,510 --> 01:14:08,590
这是真家伙
It's a real sword!

861
01:14:29,380 --> 01:14:33,450
一笑万古春
A smile ushers in the spring...

862
01:14:36,290 --> 01:14:40,180
一啼万古愁
A tear does darken all the world.

863
01:14:42,510 --> 01:14:45,760
此境 非你莫属
How truly does this befit you...

864
01:14:48,130 --> 01:14:53,950
此貌 非你莫有
Only you are possessed of such charm.

865
01:15:08,320 --> 01:15:09,160
回来
Come back.

866
01:15:11,560 --> 01:15:12,360
不要跑
Don't run!

867
01:15:35,820 --> 01:15:37,310
哎哟 嘿嘿
Ah,

868
01:15:37,400 --> 01:15:41,180
程老板 准知道你就得回来啊
Mr Cheng. I knew you'd come.

869
01:15:41,460 --> 01:15:42,890
这上座都给您留着哪
We saved a seat at the head table for you.

870
01:15:47,740 --> 01:15:48,470
小楼
Xiaolou!

871
01:15:56,700 --> 01:15:57,970
好你个蝶衣
Well if it isn't Dieyi!

872
01:15:59,260 --> 01:16:01,480
这面子 你总算给师哥了
So you've decided to give me some face at last.

873
01:16:02,870 --> 01:16:04,120
要不然
Otherwise...

874
01:16:04,520 --> 01:16:05,260
你认认
Have a look at this.

875
01:16:11,120 --> 01:16:11,950
好剑
Great sword!

876
01:16:17,560 --> 01:16:18,840
又不上台
But we're not on stage.

877
01:16:20,040 --> 01:16:21,230
要剑干什么
What would I want with a sword?

878
01:16:22,280 --> 01:16:22,860
啊
Why?

879
01:16:34,630 --> 01:16:35,480
师弟呀
Dieyi,

880
01:16:35,800 --> 01:16:37,720
今儿个 你可来晚了
you've come so late.

881
01:16:38,260 --> 01:16:39,290
该罚你一杯
I ought to punish you by making you drink this.

882
01:16:39,670 --> 01:16:41,960
对 得罚一杯
Yes, drink up!

883
01:16:51,800 --> 01:16:53,260
多谢菊仙小姐
My gratitude, Miss Juxian.

884
01:16:54,880 --> 01:16:56,830
- 啊 蝶衣 - 程老板…
- Dieyi. - Mr Cheng.

885
01:17:00,280 --> 01:17:01,060
小楼
Xiaolou,

886
01:17:02,200 --> 01:17:03,310
从今往后
from now on,

887
01:17:03,780 --> 01:17:06,630
你唱你的 我唱我的
we'll go our own ways.

888
01:17:06,930 --> 01:17:09,970
嘿 别呀 我的程老板 这可不能够
Mr Cheng, you can't do this!

889
01:17:10,500 --> 01:17:12,250
这不是 让人笑话吗
Isn't this funny?

890
01:17:12,600 --> 01:17:14,020
戏迷们 还不得要…
the fans won't...

891
01:17:14,380 --> 01:17:15,840
了...了不得
This is terrible!

892
01:17:16,780 --> 01:17:19,550
日本…日本进城 进城
Japanese troops have entered the city!

893
01:17:42,650 --> 01:17:44,250
蝶衣 蝶衣呢
Dieyi... where's Dieyi?

894
01:17:49,690 --> 01:17:54,360
“启娘娘 高力士敬酒”
I, Gao Lishi. respectfully bring you some wine

895
01:17:58,540 --> 01:18:00,770
“高力士”
Gao Lishi,

896
01:18:01,500 --> 01:18:06,720
“你敬的什么酒”
what is this wine you bring me?

897
01:18:07,690 --> 01:18:11,890
“奴牌敬的乃是通宵酒”
The wine brought by my unworthy self is called all-night wine

898
01:18:12,290 --> 01:18:15,440
“呀呀啐”
Oh dear!

899
01:18:16,580 --> 01:18:21,760
“哪个与你们通宵”
And who will spend all night with you?

900
01:18:23,210 --> 01:18:24,090
师弟说
Dieyi says...

901
01:18:25,050 --> 01:18:27,620
这眉子 得勾得立着点 才有味
the eyebrows look best if they've got a strong line.

902
01:18:30,000 --> 01:18:42,680
“人生在世如春梦”
Life's like a dream of spring

903
01:18:42,950 --> 01:18:46,090
“您那且自开怀吧”
To your heart's content!

904
01:18:47,940 --> 01:18:59,680
“且自开怀饮几盅”
I shall drink to my heart's content

905
01:19:02,680 --> 01:19:03,280
一会儿...
wait a moment...

906
01:19:03,420 --> 01:19:03,970
嗨
Yes.

907
01:19:46,400 --> 01:19:47,710
段老板 你看这个
Look at this, Mr Duan...

908
01:19:47,780 --> 01:19:48,960
太君 我给您系上
Taijun, I'll tie it for you.

909
01:19:55,240 --> 01:19:55,890
诶
Hey,

910
01:19:56,610 --> 01:19:57,250
诶
Hey,

911
01:19:58,920 --> 01:20:01,880
这不成 你得让他给我脱下来
I won't stand for it! Tell him to take it off immediately.

912
01:20:02,200 --> 01:20:02,930
小楼
Xiaolou!

913
01:20:06,680 --> 01:20:08,840
停电了…
The power is out...

914
01:20:22,340 --> 01:20:23,230
停得好啊
OK...

915
01:20:23,500 --> 01:20:27,160
好
OK...

916
01:20:27,560 --> 01:20:29,080
这才是你的戏衣
What's the fuss? It's only a costume.

917
01:20:30,010 --> 01:20:32,210
他就要你姥姥身上的寿衣
If it was the shroud out of your grandma's coffin,

918
01:20:32,460 --> 01:20:34,420
你得乖乖的给扒下来
you'd still have to give it to me.

919
01:20:35,100 --> 01:20:37,540
听明白了吗 戏子
Get my meaning? Low-life actor!

920
01:21:08,250 --> 01:21:09,980
不要怕 喔 还有什么
Don't be afraid. What else is there

921
01:21:13,290 --> 01:21:14,890
跟日本人说 我马上就去
Tell the Japanese I'll be there right away.

922
01:21:14,990 --> 01:21:16,340
诶 诶 诶 
Hey,

923
01:21:16,560 --> 01:21:17,570
慢着喔
Hold on a tick!

924
01:21:19,730 --> 01:21:21,960
这哪儿是什么堂会呀
It's not some private party.

925
01:21:22,590 --> 01:21:25,330
这就是讹您啦 去给他们唱一回去
It's a blackmail.

926
01:21:27,550 --> 01:21:30,240
您说这不去吧 眼下能救小楼的
On the one hand, you're the only one...

927
01:21:30,520 --> 01:21:31,830
除了您 没旁人了
...who can save Xiaolou.

928
01:21:32,580 --> 01:21:33,800
您要是去吧
On the other,

929
01:21:35,010 --> 01:21:37,010
万一您自个儿 再出点什么差池
if anything happened to you...

930
01:21:38,140 --> 01:21:39,680
我这个戏园子 我去...
this theatre of mine, it would...

931
01:21:41,590 --> 01:21:42,600
诶 得
All right,

932
01:21:42,870 --> 01:21:44,140
好 去 去 啊 去
All right, go then.

933
01:21:44,240 --> 01:21:46,750
诶 菊仙小姐 菊仙小姐 您干什么 小的...
Miss Juxian, what are you doing? I...

934
01:21:46,890 --> 01:21:48,390
小姐 程老板不在家
Miss, Miss... Mr Cheng isn't at home!

935
01:21:49,980 --> 01:21:50,720
蝶衣呢
Where's Dieyi? Dieyi?

936
01:21:51,390 --> 01:21:52,860
蝶衣 你赶紧的呀
Hurry!

937
01:21:53,310 --> 01:21:53,960
都说日本人
They say the Japanese...

938
01:21:53,960 --> 01:21:55,350
会放狼狗 掏人心吃
...let their dogs eat the hearts right out of people's chests.

939
01:21:56,170 --> 01:21:57,230
他又是那个脾气
And you know Xiaolou's temper.

940
01:21:57,590 --> 01:21:59,120
你要去晚了 他可就没命啦
If you delay, he mightn't have a life to save!

941
01:22:01,630 --> 01:22:02,370
师弟
Dieyi!

942
01:22:15,620 --> 01:22:19,360
我师哥 可是在您的手上 让人逮走的
But you allowed them to take him away in the first place.

943
01:22:20,700 --> 01:22:22,170
诶 你这是什么话嘛
What are you saying?

944
01:22:23,430 --> 01:22:25,090
小楼打小 是怎么待你的
Xiaolou has looked after you since you were small.

945
01:22:30,050 --> 01:22:31,350
您知道就好
Glad you're aware of that too.

946
01:22:48,690 --> 01:22:49,410
那爷
Mr Na,

947
01:22:49,500 --> 01:22:50,470
诶 嘿
Right.

948
01:22:50,570 --> 01:22:52,240
请您先退一步
would you mind leaving the room for a moment?

949
01:22:52,390 --> 01:22:52,830
诶 好
Okay!

950
01:22:52,830 --> 01:22:55,490
我跟我师弟 有几句私房话要说
I have something to say to Dieyi in private.

951
01:22:57,290 --> 01:22:59,250
都说菊仙姑娘聪明
Everyone says Miss Juxian is quite clever,

952
01:22:59,800 --> 01:23:01,110
不然不能这时候来
and her timing in this case certainly proves it.

953
01:23:02,120 --> 01:23:03,680
都是为了小楼 啊
We're all trying to help Xiaolou.

954
01:23:04,060 --> 01:23:05,750
有话好商量 诶
Talk it over.

955
01:23:09,840 --> 01:23:11,220
干脆明说了吧
How about a clear answer,

956
01:23:12,290 --> 01:23:13,940
 您倒是去 还是不去
are you going or not?

957
01:23:33,540 --> 01:23:34,460
说话呀 你
Say something!

958
01:23:44,130 --> 01:23:45,520
我明白你的心思
I know what's on your mind.

959
01:23:47,670 --> 01:23:48,650
要不这么着吧
I have a proposal.

960
01:23:50,640 --> 01:23:52,750
你只要囫囵个地 把小楼给弄出来
If you can get Xiaolou out of there in one piece,

961
01:23:53,910 --> 01:23:56,510
我哪来哪去 回我的花满楼
I'll go back to the House of Blossoms.

962
01:23:58,070 --> 01:23:59,450
躲你们俩远远的
I'll keep away from both of you then.

963
01:24:01,060 --> 01:24:01,820
成了吧
How's that?

964
01:24:05,780 --> 01:24:07,050
要说在花满楼
At the House of Blossoms,

965
01:24:08,650 --> 01:24:10,670
还真是个不操闲心的地方
you don't have to worry about much.

966
01:24:13,730 --> 01:24:15,220
日子过得轻省多了
Life is a lot simpler there.

967
01:24:22,040 --> 01:24:24,450
这可是您自个儿说的
Just remember, you said it, not me.

968
01:24:26,490 --> 01:24:27,290
一言为定
I give my word.

969
01:24:28,280 --> 01:24:52,420
“姹紫嫣红开遍”
The flowers have blossomed, Their season's past

970
01:24:53,370 --> 01:25:18,130
“似这般 都付于断井颓垣”
All has fallen, into ruin and decay

971
01:25:18,300 --> 01:25:34,000
“良辰美景奈何天”
The sun shines brightly, over the beautiful scene

972
01:25:34,220 --> 01:25:59,630
“便赏心乐事谁家院”
But is there anyone left, to enjoy it?

973
01:26:05,640 --> 01:26:07,060
- 小楼呢 - 哎呀 小楼
- Where is Xiaolou? - Xiaolou! 

974
01:26:07,500 --> 01:26:08,220
师哥
My brother!

975
01:26:10,000 --> 01:26:11,120
- 师哥 - 小楼
- Bro. - Xiaolou!

976
01:26:12,540 --> 01:26:13,260
师哥
My brother!

977
01:26:13,700 --> 01:26:15,260
小楼 你没事吧
Xiaolou, are you all right?

978
01:26:15,450 --> 01:26:16,450
你给日本人唱了
Did you sing for the Japanese?

979
01:26:16,600 --> 01:26:17,700
有个叫青木的
There's one called Aoki.

980
01:26:17,860 --> 01:26:18,970
他是懂戏的
He's quite a fan of Peking Opera

981
01:26:20,700 --> 01:26:21,460
小楼 你
Xiaolou!

982
01:27:29,640 --> 01:27:30,420
举枪
Raise a gun!

983
01:27:33,200 --> 01:27:33,910
发射
Fire!

984
01:28:08,180 --> 01:28:09,190
我好了
All right.

985
01:28:10,580 --> 01:28:11,220
来吧
Come here!

986
01:28:11,310 --> 01:28:12,450
我再喝一杯
Let me have another drink.

987
01:28:13,390 --> 01:28:15,520
对不起 我…我替你喝
I... I'll drink for you.

988
01:28:24,640 --> 01:28:25,490
嗯 来
Come on!

989
01:29:02,680 --> 01:29:04,560
这就是“霸王别姬”
I think this opera "Farewell My Concubine"

990
01:29:07,650 --> 01:29:08,670
依我之见
has turned...

991
01:29:09,890 --> 01:29:11,970
你们这戏 演到这份儿上
...into...

992
01:29:12,550 --> 01:29:14,190
竟成了姬别霸王
..."Farewell My King".

993
01:29:15,030 --> 01:29:16,470
没霸王什么看头
The king doesn't really get a look in.

994
01:29:34,920 --> 01:29:35,930
喝了它
Drink this...

995
01:29:37,310 --> 01:29:39,570
您定能纤音入云
and your voice will pierce the heavens,

996
01:29:39,990 --> 01:29:41,660
柔情胜水
yet be tender and fluid as water.

997
01:29:47,960 --> 01:29:48,960
别动
Don't move!

998
01:29:53,580 --> 01:29:54,230
好
Right.

999
01:30:30,270 --> 01:30:31,460
不唱戏了
Forget the opera.

1000
01:30:33,740 --> 01:30:34,760
往后啊
Let's just...

1001
01:30:35,720 --> 01:30:37,870
我太太平平地跟你过日子
live a quiet life.

1002
01:30:39,560 --> 01:30:41,180
再生个大胖小子
We'll have a fat little baby boy.

1003
01:30:42,350 --> 01:30:43,640
我一下得俩
And I'll have everything I want.

1004
01:30:45,420 --> 01:30:46,190
够了
That's enough.

1005
01:30:48,500 --> 01:30:49,550
不唱戏了
No more opera.

1006
01:31:23,360 --> 01:31:24,180
哎 走 走…
Let's go.

1007
01:31:24,370 --> 01:31:25,950
赶紧走 弄一个破虫子
Hurry up! Take those wretched insects!

1008
01:31:26,070 --> 01:31:27,590
大哥 我走了 再见啊
See you, pal.

1009
01:31:27,590 --> 01:31:28,390
行了 行了…
All right, all right!

1010
01:31:29,630 --> 01:31:30,300
嘿
Hey,

1011
01:31:31,690 --> 01:31:32,460
拿出来
Hand it over!

1012
01:31:33,800 --> 01:31:35,230
谁要你这破蛐蛐
I'm not talking about your stupid crickets.

1013
01:31:35,960 --> 01:31:36,870
你借他的钱呢
Where's the money he lent you?

1014
01:31:37,030 --> 01:31:37,870
我这是...
I...

1015
01:31:38,440 --> 01:31:40,430
你别看他今儿个高兴 想讹他
Don't think you can take advantage of him when he's in a good mood.

1016
01:31:41,130 --> 01:31:43,390
把钱拿出来 赶紧的
Give me the money and get lost.

1017
01:31:45,830 --> 01:31:48,290
玩蛐蛐 大爷乐意
I'm the one who wanted them.

1018
01:31:49,520 --> 01:31:50,270
赶紧走吧
Piss off!

1019
01:31:54,830 --> 01:31:56,820
站起来 都是七尺高的老爷们儿
A man's no longer a man if he gives up a proper job

1020
01:31:57,550 --> 01:31:58,990
放正经营生 不做
to waste all his time...

1021
01:31:59,270 --> 01:32:00,950
在一个小虫子身上找饭摺
...on these stupid insects.

1022
01:32:01,300 --> 01:32:01,990
德行
Disgusting!

1023
01:32:04,200 --> 01:32:05,360
正经营生
A proper job?

1024
01:32:06,170 --> 01:32:07,590
我姓段的就会唱戏
All I can do is sing

1025
01:32:08,220 --> 01:32:09,940
啊 戏你不让我唱了
and you won't stand for that.

1026
01:32:10,250 --> 01:32:11,660
我不玩蛐蛐 我干嘛去啊
What am I supposed to do?

1027
01:32:12,630 --> 01:32:14,080
我抬棺材 掏大粪去
Find work as a pallbearer? A night soil carrier?

1028
01:32:14,430 --> 01:32:15,040
我...
I...

1029
01:32:16,180 --> 01:32:16,860
我放...
I throw...

1030
01:32:19,170 --> 01:32:21,770
得 这下您乐了吧
Would that make you happy?

1031
01:32:23,910 --> 01:32:24,770
瞧你
Look at you!

1032
01:32:26,410 --> 01:32:27,330
真生气啦
You're really angry?

1033
01:32:28,500 --> 01:32:29,220
拿着
Take this back.

1034
01:32:30,840 --> 01:32:31,780
你还没完啦
Not through yet?

1035
01:32:33,960 --> 01:32:34,680
得
Right.

1036
01:32:35,300 --> 01:32:36,780
算我话说重了 成了吧
So I overstated things a bit. OK?

1037
01:32:38,100 --> 01:32:40,050
哎 你要是不这么着啊
If you're not careful,

1038
01:32:40,620 --> 01:32:43,440
他们就像那狗尿苔似的 长咱们家了
these people will be all over us like fungus.

1039
01:32:45,580 --> 01:32:46,620
诶
Hey,

1040
01:32:46,620 --> 01:32:48,700
科班那个 关老爷子说 让你去哪
Oh, your old teacher wants you to go see him.

1041
01:32:49,590 --> 01:32:51,560
不去 没脸见师傅
I'm not going. I'm too ashamed of myself.

1042
01:32:58,440 --> 01:33:05,320
“看那剑”
Look at that sword!

1043
01:33:11,290 --> 01:33:13,670
老爷子 他们都到了
Sir, they're here!

1044
01:33:15,480 --> 01:33:16,360
谁呀
Who?

1045
01:33:16,700 --> 01:33:17,950
蝶衣 小楼
Dieyi and Xiaolou.

1046
01:33:18,260 --> 01:33:21,450
您一叫 他们立马就来 看您来啦
They came as soon as they heard you wanted to see them.

1047
01:33:21,820 --> 01:33:25,040
哎哟 这可怎么了不得了
Oh, this really is something!

1048
01:33:25,140 --> 01:33:25,630
师傅
Master!

1049
01:33:25,630 --> 01:33:28,240
是两位角儿来啦
The two famous actors are here!

1050
01:33:28,240 --> 01:33:28,810
徒弟该死
We are unworthy of you.

1051
01:33:28,810 --> 01:33:29,800
哎哟
Ah.

1052
01:33:29,950 --> 01:33:33,450
- 师父 - 我这面子天大了去啦
- Master, - You really have given me a lot of face.

1053
01:33:33,600 --> 01:33:34,300
哎
Ah.

1054
01:33:34,440 --> 01:33:36,350
我这怎么当得起
I'm deeply honoured.

1055
01:33:36,530 --> 01:33:37,870
啊 请坐 请坐
Please, have a seat.

1056
01:33:38,190 --> 01:33:40,680
受老朽一拜啊
Let this decrepit old man pay his respects.

1057
01:33:41,150 --> 01:33:42,000
徒弟不敢
Master, your students wouldn't presume...

1058
01:33:46,450 --> 01:33:47,530
不敢
Wouldn't presume!

1059
01:33:49,030 --> 01:33:51,120
而今 什么你们不敢
What wouldn't you presume?

1060
01:33:53,300 --> 01:33:54,580
程蝶衣
Cheng Dieyi,

1061
01:33:56,640 --> 01:34:01,780
当初 是你师哥把你 成全出来的
Cheng Dieyi, Xiaolou helped make you what you are today.

1062
01:34:03,240 --> 01:34:07,090
现在 你师哥不唱戏了
Now he's not singing anymore.

1063
01:34:08,850 --> 01:34:12,700
你也该拉他一把吧
It's time for you to give him a hand.

1064
01:34:17,130 --> 01:34:18,460
快着点啊
Come on!

1065
01:34:27,650 --> 01:34:29,320
给我动手啊
Do it!

1066
01:34:41,730 --> 01:34:43,170
小豆子
Little Douzi!

1067
01:34:44,660 --> 01:34:46,280
小石头
Little Shitou!

1068
01:34:48,570 --> 01:34:51,520
你们俩起小 这点故事
There's been a lot of water under the bridge

1069
01:34:52,650 --> 01:34:55,100
话说来长啦
since you were children.

1070
01:34:58,530 --> 01:34:59,440
怎么啊
Now,

1071
01:35:00,240 --> 01:35:03,890
现在成角儿了 谱大了
you're great actors. You're too big for your britches.

1072
01:35:04,770 --> 01:35:05,450
啊
Why?

1073
01:35:06,170 --> 01:35:07,540
就什么都忘了
But have you forgotten?

1074
01:35:08,730 --> 01:35:13,380
到了这个时候 就不忍心 啊
Don't you have the heart for it anymore?

1075
01:35:19,410 --> 01:35:23,370
你要喜欢就纵着他 不许护着他
Did I tell you to spoil and indulge him?

1076
01:35:24,380 --> 01:35:25,870
我叫你看着他
Did I tell you to sit by...

1077
01:35:26,180 --> 01:35:27,060
糟塌戏
while he wastes his talents?

1078
01:35:27,250 --> 01:35:28,140
诶 诶
Hey, hey.

1079
01:35:28,580 --> 01:35:29,950
我叫你看着他
Did I tell you to cover up for him?

1080
01:35:32,000 --> 01:35:33,460
- 我来 师傅 - 糟塌戏
- Master! - To desecrate the opera!

1081
01:35:33,630 --> 01:35:34,410
师傅
Master...

1082
01:35:35,850 --> 01:35:36,810
是我没出息
It's me who's the no-hoper.

1083
01:35:38,340 --> 01:35:39,170
您打我
Punish me!

1084
01:35:40,560 --> 01:35:41,680
老爷子
Listen to me, Grandpa,

1085
01:35:42,860 --> 01:35:44,190
您猜怎么着
can you guess what I have to say?

1086
01:35:44,990 --> 01:35:47,360
现而今 小楼可是我的人了
Xiaolou belongs to me these days,

1087
01:35:48,020 --> 01:35:49,000
您打他也成
If you want to hit him,

1088
01:35:49,630 --> 01:35:50,910
您得先告我一声呀
If you want to hit him, you've got to notify me first.

1089
01:35:50,910 --> 01:35:51,640
菊仙
Juxian!

1090
01:35:52,010 --> 01:35:53,170
哟
Oh,

1091
01:35:53,420 --> 01:35:57,240
您是花满楼那姑娘不是
It's that girl from the House of Blossoms, isn't it?

1092
01:35:57,450 --> 01:36:01,660
唉哟 您今儿个可是第一位贵客
Today, you are our number one guest.

1093
01:36:01,880 --> 01:36:03,780
您可得坐好
Make yourself comfortable.

1094
01:36:03,940 --> 01:36:08,520
喝好啊 看好了再去
Have a drink and a look around.

1095
01:36:10,320 --> 01:36:11,210
您请
Please!

1096
01:36:18,700 --> 01:36:20,700
- 我叫你吃喝嫖赌  - 打得好
- Did I teach you to eat, drink, - Good! I deserve it!

1097
01:36:21,940 --> 01:36:24,100
- 我叫你玩蛐蛐  - 打得好
- go whoring and gamble? Play with crickets? - Good! I deserve it!

1098
01:36:25,080 --> 01:36:26,560
我叫你当行头
Did I teach you to pawn your costumes?

1099
01:36:26,660 --> 01:36:27,560
师傅保重
Master take care!

1100
01:36:28,340 --> 01:36:29,920
- 我叫你糟塌戏  - 打得好
- To desecrate the opera! - Good! I deserve it!

1101
01:36:31,390 --> 01:36:32,320
哎呀 打得好
Good! I deserve it!

1102
01:36:32,620 --> 01:36:33,520
诶 打得好
Good! I deserve it!

1103
01:36:33,820 --> 01:36:34,760
诶 打得好
Good! I deserve it!

1104
01:36:36,410 --> 01:36:37,200
慢着
Hold on!

1105
01:36:38,880 --> 01:36:40,840
这当师哥的糟塌戏
If he's desecrating the opera,

1106
01:36:41,540 --> 01:36:42,850
您活该打他
you ought to punish him.

1107
01:36:44,300 --> 01:36:46,240
可这当师弟的这个
But don't you figure his stage brother...

1108
01:36:47,450 --> 01:36:50,170
请问您 这算什么
...has a gesture in it as well?

1109
01:36:50,380 --> 01:36:51,120
菊仙
Juxian!

1110
01:36:54,480 --> 01:36:56,010
我既是花满楼的
I'm from the House of Blossoms.

1111
01:36:56,640 --> 01:36:59,080
自然不归 你们喜福成科班的管
This is none of my business,

1112
01:37:00,570 --> 01:37:02,200
可是您这当师傅的
but as their teacher,

1113
01:37:02,640 --> 01:37:04,540
也不能只听一面之词不是
shouldn't you listen to both sides of the story?

1114
01:37:04,540 --> 01:37:05,210
闭嘴
Shut up!

1115
01:37:06,310 --> 01:37:08,040
老爷们儿的事 没你说话的份儿
This is between us men! Keep out of it!

1116
01:37:22,460 --> 01:37:23,330
段小楼
Duan Xiaolou,

1117
01:37:24,930 --> 01:37:26,770
你可真知道疼人啦
you really are a tender soul!

1118
01:37:28,360 --> 01:37:29,050
再打呀
Hit me again!

1119
01:37:29,150 --> 01:37:30,350
你再胡唚
If you don't shut up,

1120
01:37:30,890 --> 01:37:32,020
我他妈打死你
I'll kill you.

1121
01:37:32,730 --> 01:37:34,930
- 诶 别 别介… - 别拦着我
- Don't! - Don't stop me!

1122
01:37:35,700 --> 01:37:36,670
好啊
Good.

1123
01:37:37,650 --> 01:37:41,350
今儿个 你打死我 算你赚了一个
Do that. You'll take two lives at once.

1124
01:37:44,040 --> 01:37:46,040
让你老段家 断子绝孙去吧
The Duan family line will stop with you!

1125
01:37:50,200 --> 01:37:50,940
诶
Why?

1126
01:37:51,410 --> 01:37:52,870
谁让你们俩 站起来的
Who told you to stand up?

1127
01:37:54,270 --> 01:37:55,070
哼 嘿 嘿
Heh heh heh.

1128
01:37:56,430 --> 01:37:57,430
小石头
Shitou,

1129
01:37:58,140 --> 01:37:59,580
听见了没有啊
are you paying attention?

1130
01:37:59,900 --> 01:38:00,640
啊
Ah,

1131
01:38:00,860 --> 01:38:03,090
你也是个快当爹的人了
You're going to be a father.

1132
01:38:04,380 --> 01:38:06,810
这么瞎混下去 丢了玩艺儿
If you keep wasting your time and lose your skills,

1133
01:38:06,960 --> 01:38:11,110
你以后 你拿什么请我 喝满月酒啊
how are you going to afford a celebration banquet for the birth?

1134
01:38:12,830 --> 01:38:13,610
跪近点
Kneel closer to one another!

1135
01:38:17,120 --> 01:38:18,730
再靠紧着点儿
Closer!

1136
01:38:29,210 --> 01:38:30,410
好好练 好好练
Work harder!

1137
01:38:32,670 --> 01:38:33,530
都拿稳了
Get a good grip!

1138
01:38:34,980 --> 01:38:37,520
腿伸直了 给我绷直了
Stretch those legs! Stretch!

1139
01:38:41,500 --> 01:38:42,270
仰起头
Raise your head.

1140
01:38:50,530 --> 01:38:51,470
慢着 慢着
Wait a minute!

1141
01:38:54,270 --> 01:38:56,170
你练的这是"夜奔"
You're practising "Fleeing by Night," aren't you?

1142
01:38:57,290 --> 01:38:58,450
扮的是林冲
You're playing Lin Chong.

1143
01:38:58,920 --> 01:39:00,050
林冲什么人呐
Who's this Lin Chong?

1144
01:39:01,070 --> 01:39:03,300
那是八十万禁军教头
He's head of the palace guard,

1145
01:39:03,780 --> 01:39:04,810
不是小毛贼
not some sneaky little thief.

1146
01:39:06,040 --> 01:39:06,740
拿着
Take this.

1147
01:39:08,020 --> 01:39:09,060
都瞧我的
Attention everyone!

1148
01:39:10,200 --> 01:39:13,490
看看什么是 盖世英雄
This is what a great hero's like.

1149
01:39:17,690 --> 01:39:23,950
“丈夫有泪不轻弹”
A man doesn't lightly shed hi tears...

1150
01:39:25,820 --> 01:39:39,300
“只因未到伤心处”
Unless his heart has broken.

1151
01:40:52,270 --> 01:40:52,970
别动
Don't!

1152
01:40:53,200 --> 01:40:54,540
师傅罚我七天都跪
The teacher told me to kneel for seven days as punishment,

1153
01:40:54,760 --> 01:40:55,790
还没到日子呢
time's not up yet!

1154
01:40:56,110 --> 01:40:57,100
科班都散了
The troupe has disbanded...

1155
01:40:58,500 --> 01:40:59,610
你还傻跪什么呀
What's the point of this idiotic kneeling?

1156
01:40:59,740 --> 01:41:01,550
师傅说了 要想成角儿
Master said that only you have the power...

1157
01:41:01,680 --> 01:41:03,020
就得自个儿 成全自个儿
...to make yourself a great actor.

1158
01:41:03,900 --> 01:41:05,030
旁人都走了
Everyone else has left.

1159
01:41:07,270 --> 01:41:08,050
你也家去吧
You ought to go home too.

1160
01:41:08,150 --> 01:41:09,310
我打小被捡回来的
I was found on the street as a baby.

1161
01:41:09,420 --> 01:41:10,140
没家
I've got no other home.

1162
01:41:13,830 --> 01:41:15,330
没告诉谁捡的你
Do you know who found you?

1163
01:41:15,770 --> 01:41:16,480
没告诉
No!

1164
01:41:16,590 --> 01:41:17,810
说怕我知道了是谁
They said if I knew I'd get a big head...

1165
01:41:18,000 --> 01:41:19,180
犯狂 不用功
...and wouldn't work hard.

1166
01:41:21,480 --> 01:41:22,350
还想唱戏吗
Do you still want to sing opera?

1167
01:41:22,810 --> 01:41:25,010
唱 要饭也唱 要成角儿
Yes, even if I have to beg to support myself!

1168
01:41:30,290 --> 01:41:31,080
你叫什么
What's your name?

1169
01:41:34,010 --> 01:41:34,720
小四
Xiao Si.

1170
01:41:39,810 --> 01:41:40,530
小四
Xiao Si.

1171
01:42:39,040 --> 01:42:46,840
“只听得众兵丁们议论”
I hear the talk of the soldiers

1172
01:42:48,570 --> 01:42:51,700
四儿 你下去跟经理说 别闹出事来
Xiao Si, go tell the manager to avoid trouble.

1173
01:42:51,880 --> 01:42:52,490
诶
Yes.

1174
01:42:52,840 --> 01:43:01,900
“口声声露出了离散之心”
And it is all about running away

1175
01:43:05,180 --> 01:43:06,780
嘿 怎么不唱了
What's this? Why aren't you singing?

1176
01:43:10,110 --> 01:43:10,750
别乱
Don't make trouble!

1177
01:43:20,250 --> 01:43:21,840
诶诶 小楼 去不得啊
Don't go, Xiaolou.

1178
01:43:21,950 --> 01:43:22,780
诶 快去追啊
It's not worth it!

1179
01:43:43,500 --> 01:43:44,340
各位老总
Soldiers! Gentlemen!

1180
01:43:48,490 --> 01:43:49,780
这戏园子里头
You can't just wave your...

1181
01:43:50,420 --> 01:43:52,660
没有用手电筒 晃人的规矩
...flashlights around in the theatre.

1182
01:43:53,570 --> 01:43:55,250
连日本人 也没那么闹过
Even the Japanese didn't do this sort of thing.

1183
01:43:56,350 --> 01:43:57,790
大伙儿都是来听戏的
Everyone's here for the opera.

1184
01:43:58,680 --> 01:43:59,860
请回座上去吧
Please return to your seats.

1185
01:44:04,510 --> 01:44:05,480
说得好
All right.

1186
01:44:06,490 --> 01:44:07,290
回去
Seats, everyone!

1187
01:44:11,080 --> 01:44:12,130
可是有一样
But...

1188
01:44:12,890 --> 01:44:15,040
替日本人叫好 成不成
can we let him get away with speaking up for the Japanese?

1189
01:44:15,160 --> 01:44:16,130
不成
No!

1190
01:44:16,270 --> 01:44:17,020
打
Get him!

1191
01:44:20,090 --> 01:44:21,610
我操你大爷
Fuck your mother!

1192
01:44:27,460 --> 01:44:28,250
小楼
Xiaolou!

1193
01:44:30,300 --> 01:44:31,080
小楼
Xiaolou!

1194
01:44:32,990 --> 01:44:33,880
小楼
Xiaolou!

1195
01:44:37,670 --> 01:44:38,500
小楼
Xiaolou!

1196
01:44:51,430 --> 01:44:52,300
你放开他
Leave him alone!

1197
01:44:52,450 --> 01:44:54,110
你放开他 放开他
Leave him alone!

1198
01:44:54,640 --> 01:44:55,340
放开
Leave him alone!

1199
01:45:06,700 --> 01:45:07,960
喂 菊仙
Juxian!

1200
01:45:09,380 --> 01:45:11,940
快...快
Hurry!

1201
01:45:12,450 --> 01:45:13,330
有我在这儿
I'm here,

1202
01:45:13,940 --> 01:45:14,590
菊仙
Juxian...

1203
01:45:15,550 --> 01:45:17,220
快 快 凳子…
Get her a stool. Hurry!

1204
01:45:19,860 --> 01:45:20,990
您瞧 段太太呢
Mrs Duan has to get to hospital.

1205
01:45:22,210 --> 01:45:23,720
- 赶紧送医院 先保住大人再说 - 好
- Save her first and worry about the baby later. - Right.

1206
01:45:23,820 --> 01:45:24,760
赶紧着呀
Hurry!

1207
01:45:29,330 --> 01:45:30,100
让开
Let us through!

1208
01:45:30,610 --> 01:45:31,360
让开
Let us through!

1209
01:45:34,190 --> 01:45:35,390
诶呦嚯 嘿
Hey, hey, hey

1210
01:45:35,570 --> 01:45:38,130
瞧不就是公共治安 这么大点事吗
There was only a minor disturbance.

1211
01:45:38,240 --> 01:45:41,210
还至于 至于劳动诸位 弄出这么大的动静
Such a show of force, is it really necessary?

1212
01:45:41,650 --> 01:45:42,670
要动罚款
To be fined.

1213
01:45:42,980 --> 01:45:43,730
噢 罚款
You can fine us.

1214
01:46:02,100 --> 01:46:03,450
还要抓人呐
Why do you need to arrest anyone?

1215
01:46:04,350 --> 01:46:05,440
这戏园子砸了
The theatre's been trashed,

1216
01:46:05,630 --> 01:46:07,300
人也快打死了 你们还要抓人呐
people beaten, and you still want to arrest him?

1217
01:46:07,490 --> 01:46:08,340
可不 可不能够怪他
We can't blame him.

1218
01:46:08,340 --> 01:46:09,170
快把他放开
Let him go!

1219
01:46:10,800 --> 01:46:11,440
走
Move!

1220
01:46:12,020 --> 01:46:12,930
数他狠
He's ruthless

1221
01:46:13,650 --> 01:46:14,320
你直说
You speak up!

1222
01:46:14,400 --> 01:46:15,780
这点钱 嘿嘿 辛苦了
This money... Thank you!

1223
01:46:16,960 --> 01:46:18,140
你们凭什么抓人
Why?

1224
01:46:20,740 --> 01:46:21,650
凭什么
What for?

1225
01:46:23,670 --> 01:46:25,860
程蝶衣犯的是汉奸罪
Cheng Dieyi betrayed the country to the Japanese.

1226
01:46:28,880 --> 01:46:29,510
走
Move it!

1227
01:46:30,680 --> 01:46:32,130
你们凭什么 说他是汉奸
How can you say that about him?

1228
01:46:34,050 --> 01:46:35,000
师傅
Teacher,

1229
01:46:35,730 --> 01:46:36,260
师傅
Teacher,

1230
01:46:36,260 --> 01:46:37,600
你凭什么说他是汉奸
How can you say that about him?

1231
01:46:37,600 --> 01:46:38,430
段老板
Mr Duan!

1232
01:46:39,940 --> 01:46:40,740
段老板
Mr Duan,

1233
01:46:41,530 --> 01:46:44,170
孩子怕是保不住了
I'm afraid she's lost the baby.

1234
01:46:53,570 --> 01:46:54,530
小楼
Xiaolou,

1235
01:46:56,480 --> 01:46:57,800
我真对不住你
I'm so sorry.

1236
01:47:01,010 --> 01:47:02,150
你忙你的去
Go do what you have to do.

1237
01:47:25,640 --> 01:47:26,890
你这师弟呀
I don't know whether...

1238
01:47:27,600 --> 01:47:30,530
也不知道这世道 跟他找别扭呢
...Dieyi goes looking for trouble...

1239
01:47:31,620 --> 01:47:33,220
还是他跟这个世道 找别扭
...or if it's trouble that comes looking for him.

1240
01:47:34,640 --> 01:47:35,920
总是轻省不了
But there seems no avoiding it.

1241
01:47:36,290 --> 01:47:37,540
早晚还得出乱子
Sooner or later, he'll come to grief.

1242
01:47:38,920 --> 01:47:40,220
只要你跟他在一起
Whenever you're with him,

1243
01:47:42,010 --> 01:47:43,300
我这心里 就不踏实
my heart's in my throat.

1244
01:47:48,420 --> 01:47:49,760
咱们的孩子没了
Now I've lost our child,

1245
01:47:52,750 --> 01:47:54,330
我可就剩你一人了
you're all I have left.

1246
01:47:55,380 --> 01:47:58,130
往后跟你一起去要饭 我都没二话
I don't care if I have to beg with you on the streets,

1247
01:47:59,960 --> 01:48:00,980
可就有一样
all I ask...

1248
01:48:02,350 --> 01:48:03,120
小楼
Xiaolou,

1249
01:48:05,140 --> 01:48:07,760
你得让我这心里 太太平平的
all I ask is peace of mind.

1250
01:48:13,730 --> 01:48:14,970
你把他救出来了
If you help him now,

1251
01:48:15,170 --> 01:48:16,670
咱们可就不欠他的了
we'll no longer owe him anything.

1252
01:48:17,240 --> 01:48:18,590
往后你别跟他唱了
Don't perform with him anymore.

1253
01:48:21,800 --> 01:48:22,810
你答应我
Promise me this.

1254
01:48:24,540 --> 01:48:25,920
你得给我立字据呀
Put it in writing.

1255
01:48:26,170 --> 01:48:26,890
啊
Ok?

1256
01:48:54,830 --> 01:48:55,520
四爷
Master Yuan,

1257
01:48:57,130 --> 01:48:58,900
蝶衣这条性命
Dieyi's life...

1258
01:48:59,470 --> 01:49:01,760
可就全仰仗您啦
...in your hands.

1259
01:49:03,070 --> 01:49:04,760
这点 您先打点着
Count this.

1260
01:49:05,470 --> 01:49:08,180
但凡不够 咱们回头再… 是吧
If it's not enough...

1261
01:49:08,290 --> 01:49:10,010
- 啊 - 诶 诶 哼
- Oh. - Yes.

1262
01:49:10,430 --> 01:49:11,200
袁四爷
Master Yuan,

1263
01:49:12,120 --> 01:49:13,560
您只要是救出蝶衣
If only you'll save Dieyi,

1264
01:49:14,570 --> 01:49:17,380
我们哥俩三年的包银 全归了您
we'll give you all our earnings for the next three years.

1265
01:49:17,760 --> 01:49:18,410
哼
Hum.

1266
01:49:18,810 --> 01:49:21,740
没你们的包银 你当我就喂不起这几只鸟啊
You think I need your money to keep my birds from starving?

1267
01:49:27,260 --> 01:49:28,180
这位是
And this gentleman is...?

1268
01:49:30,890 --> 01:49:32,170
这不小楼吗
Don't you recognise Xiaolou?

1269
01:49:32,570 --> 01:49:33,360
那什么
What's that,

1270
01:49:35,370 --> 01:49:37,820
给蝶衣唱霸王 那段小楼啊
He plays the king to Dieyi's concubine.

1271
01:49:41,080 --> 01:49:42,720
那该他救虞姬去呀
Then it should be he who saves Concubine Yu!

1272
01:49:44,520 --> 01:49:47,160
呀 我的亲老爷子呐 那不是戏吗
My dear man, that's only a play!

1273
01:49:48,050 --> 01:49:49,430
可着全北平
All Peiping knows that...

1274
01:49:49,920 --> 01:49:52,860
谁不知道袁四爷 才是梨园行的真霸王呀
...Master Yuan is the true king of the theatre!

1275
01:49:53,410 --> 01:49:54,120
是吗
Is that so?

1276
01:49:54,380 --> 01:49:55,830
噢 是 是
It's true.

1277
01:49:56,380 --> 01:49:57,050
是
It's true.

1278
01:49:57,170 --> 01:50:00,130
诶 这说到戏 我倒要请教段老板
Speaking of theatre, I'd like to ask Mr Duan something.

1279
01:50:01,760 --> 01:50:05,150
这霸王回营亮过相 去见这虞姬
When the king returns to see Concubine Yu...

1280
01:50:07,540 --> 01:50:09,150
到底该走几步啊
How many steps should he take?

1281
01:50:13,100 --> 01:50:13,850
七步
Seven.

1282
01:50:14,800 --> 01:50:15,800
走我瞧瞧
Show me.

1283
01:50:20,260 --> 01:50:21,290
走我瞧瞧呀
Come on, show me!

1284
01:50:23,520 --> 01:50:24,230
四爷
Master Yuan...

1285
01:50:28,210 --> 01:50:30,130
诶 这是什么 什么 干吗啊
What is this for?  What are you doing?

1286
01:50:33,210 --> 01:50:35,340
这是袁四爷的府上吧
Is this the honourable home of Master Yuan?

1287
01:50:39,550 --> 01:50:41,090
有位叫程蝶衣的
When a man called Cheng Dieyi...

1288
01:50:42,010 --> 01:50:43,920
让人逮走的时候 说是
was arrested, he said...

1289
01:50:45,020 --> 01:50:46,870
这把剑的主人能救他
the owner of this sword would be able to rescue him.

1290
01:50:48,690 --> 01:50:49,570
您瞅瞅
Have a look,

1291
01:50:50,920 --> 01:50:51,740
认得吗
Do you recognise it?

1292
01:51:06,040 --> 01:51:07,400
瞧您这意思
From your expression,

1293
01:51:08,220 --> 01:51:09,440
我是找对主儿了
I see I've come to the right place.

1294
01:51:11,640 --> 01:51:12,370
那成
Good.

1295
01:51:13,080 --> 01:51:15,830
这剑呐 我给您搁这儿啦
I'll put the sword here.

1296
01:51:16,440 --> 01:51:17,080
啊
Oh.

1297
01:51:17,500 --> 01:51:21,120
这剑找着主儿 我也就放心了
I'm so relieved to have found its owner.

1298
01:51:27,080 --> 01:51:30,250
可这人哪 也总有指望错的时候
But sometimes one's hopes are misplaced.

1299
01:51:31,380 --> 01:51:32,330
袁四爷
Master Yuan,

1300
01:51:33,580 --> 01:51:35,310
您可别怪罪蝶衣呀
you mustn't blame Dieyi.

1301
01:51:40,240 --> 01:51:42,060
诶 弄明白啰
Hey, I see.

1302
01:51:44,040 --> 01:51:45,680
他给日本人唱堂会
He didn't say I...

1303
01:51:46,040 --> 01:51:47,120
怕不是袁…
I put him up to it,

1304
01:51:48,780 --> 01:51:50,040
袁某的指使吧
did he?

1305
01:51:50,340 --> 01:51:51,100
哟
Oh,

1306
01:51:52,040 --> 01:51:54,180
要是您袁四爷 让他去的
If you were involved,

1307
01:51:54,790 --> 01:51:56,690
他能让人给逮起来吗
he wouldn't be in trouble, would he?

1308
01:51:58,160 --> 01:51:58,880
那是
True!

1309
01:52:04,550 --> 01:52:05,200
诶
Oh dear!

1310
01:52:05,290 --> 01:52:07,560
一屋的记者 都在家里等着呢
There's a roomful of reporters waiting at home.

1311
01:52:07,900 --> 01:52:09,160
- 小楼 那爷 - 诶
- Xiaolou, Mr Na, - Ok.

1312
01:52:09,260 --> 01:52:09,880
咱们走
Xiaolou, Mr Na, let's go.

1313
01:52:09,880 --> 01:52:12,200
- 诶 别 别 慢着 话说清楚啰 - 那爷
- Wait a moment! Let's talk. -  Mr Na.

1314
01:52:21,700 --> 01:52:23,500
袁四爷让我来关照你
Master Yuan asked me to talk to you.

1315
01:52:26,290 --> 01:52:27,660
赶明儿个上了法庭
Tomorrow in court,

1316
01:52:28,610 --> 01:52:31,710
你得说是日本人 拿枪逼着你 去唱的堂会
say the Japanese put a gun to your head.

1317
01:52:32,740 --> 01:52:34,880
在兵营里头 给你动了刑
Say they tortured you.

1318
01:52:36,040 --> 01:52:38,880
旁的 袁四爷都替你安排妥当了
Master Yuan has made arrangements for everything else.

1319
01:52:49,210 --> 01:52:50,980
这是小楼让我交给你的
This is from Xiaolou.

1320
01:53:01,710 --> 01:53:03,750
蝶衣 你别怨我们
Dieyi, don't be angry with us.

1321
01:53:04,540 --> 01:53:05,770
小楼的孩子
The death of...

1322
01:53:11,000 --> 01:53:12,070
死了
...Xiaolou's child...

1323
01:53:16,580 --> 01:53:18,870
这就是你们在一块儿唱戏的报应
was karmic retribution for your partnership.

1324
01:53:29,210 --> 01:53:30,260
出去以后
After you get out of here,

1325
01:53:32,240 --> 01:53:34,000
你走你的阳关道 去吧
just go your own way.

1326
01:53:40,550 --> 01:53:46,380
查伶人程蝶衣 在我中华民国 对日抗战时期
During the War of Resistance against the Japanese,

1327
01:53:46,940 --> 01:53:51,480
竟与日寇驻平警备旅团之敌酋 青木三郎
the accused, Cheng Dieyi, performed pornographic works

1328
01:53:51,870 --> 01:53:55,420
互通款曲 狼狈为奸
for the Japanese troops under Aoki Saburo.

1329
01:53:55,820 --> 01:54:00,440
以淫词艳曲 为日寇作堂会演出
Cheng and Aoki expressed mutual affection and acted in collusion,

1330
01:54:01,050 --> 01:54:04,560
长敌之气焰 灭我之尊严
boosting enemy morale and damaging national self-respect.

1331
01:54:06,590 --> 01:54:09,130
敌酋青木三郎 在日军投降后
After the Japanese surrender, Aoki refused to give up

1332
01:54:09,340 --> 01:54:12,600
仍有反抗举动 已被我军击毙
and was shot dead by our troops.

1333
01:54:13,230 --> 01:54:17,310
其与被告往来之罪证相片 已落入我方
His association with the accused is well documented in photographs. 

1334
01:54:18,160 --> 01:54:21,540
现出示法庭 铁证如山
The evidence is ironclad.

1335
01:54:23,780 --> 01:54:24,580
传...
We call on...

1336
01:54:25,800 --> 01:54:27,520
证人 袁世卿
the witnesses Yuan Shiqing,

1337
01:54:27,940 --> 01:54:29,180
段小楼
Duan Xiaolou...

1338
01:54:29,540 --> 01:54:31,040
那坤 出庭
and Na Kun.

1339
01:54:39,170 --> 01:54:41,380
世卿世受国恩
The government has always been good to me.

1340
