1533
02:09:00,110 --> 02:09:00,830
别闹
Stop carrying on!

1534
02:09:09,970 --> 02:09:10,680
听着
Listening!

1535
02:09:12,430 --> 02:09:13,220
你听着
You listen!

1536
02:09:14,220 --> 02:09:16,160
再忍忍就过去了 听见没有
Are you listening? You'll get over it with time.

1537
02:09:16,660 --> 02:09:17,980
好了 别闹了
Good, calm down.

1538
02:09:18,280 --> 02:09:19,080
再忍忍 就过去了
Everything will be OK.

1539
02:09:19,080 --> 02:09:20,390
我操你大爷
Fuck you!

1540
02:09:22,470 --> 02:09:23,360
别闹了
Cut it out!

1541
02:09:25,490 --> 02:09:26,200
别闹了
Cut it out!

1542
02:09:26,420 --> 02:09:27,690
再闹 我就打你了
Cut it out or I'll hit you!

1543
02:09:27,690 --> 02:09:28,780
- 给我 - 别闹了
- Give it to me. - No kidding,

1544
02:09:34,570 --> 02:09:35,640
放开我
let me go!

1545
02:09:47,810 --> 02:09:48,620
不要动
Don't move!

1546
02:09:53,450 --> 02:09:54,170
怎么着
How is he?

1547
02:09:54,420 --> 02:09:55,540
看样子 得用点药
I think we'll have to give him some drugs.

1548
02:09:56,090 --> 02:09:56,880
你看着点
Keep an eye on him.

1549
02:09:57,410 --> 02:09:58,230
别让他挣蹦出来
Don't let him hurt himself.

1550
02:09:58,330 --> 02:10:00,310
诶 小楼 你可别走啊
Don't go, Xiaolou.

1551
02:10:00,390 --> 02:10:02,520
无碍的 他要想把大烟戒了
If he really wants to overcome his addiction to opium,

1552
02:10:02,890 --> 02:10:04,680
还得脱几层皮呢 这才是个头
he's going to have to go through hell! This is just the start.

1553
02:10:04,860 --> 02:10:05,550
诶
Hey.

1554
02:10:45,170 --> 02:10:45,960
我冷
I'm cold!

1555
02:10:52,270 --> 02:10:53,000
娘
Ma!

1556
02:10:55,050 --> 02:10:56,820
水都冻冰了
The water's all turned to ice!

1557
02:11:00,720 --> 02:11:01,580
我冷
I'm cold!

1558
02:11:06,110 --> 02:11:06,970
娘
Ma!

1559
02:11:08,870 --> 02:11:10,560
水都冻冰了
The water's all turned to ice!

1560
02:11:14,140 --> 02:11:14,920
我冷
I'm cold...

1561
02:11:18,570 --> 02:11:19,590
好了 好了
It's OK. Everything's all right.

1562
02:11:28,360 --> 02:11:30,820
“解放军的天是晴明的天”
The sky of the liberated areas is clear and blue

1563
02:11:31,290 --> 02:11:33,370
“解放区的人民好喜欢”
The people of the liberated areas are happy...

1564
02:11:38,430 --> 02:11:39,230
段师母
Mrs Duan!

1565
02:11:41,870 --> 02:11:42,820
你到哪儿去了
Where were you?

1566
02:11:43,800 --> 02:11:44,680
开会去了
A meeting.

1567
02:11:45,930 --> 02:11:46,670
开会去了
A meeting?

1568
02:11:46,750 --> 02:11:47,420
诶
Yes.

1569
02:11:54,910 --> 02:11:56,470
小楼 师兄师弟们都来了
Xiaolou, the whole troupe's come.

1570
02:11:56,470 --> 02:11:57,150
诶 快请进
Come on in. Quick!

1571
02:11:57,150 --> 02:11:58,080
进来 进来啊
Come in! Come in!

1572
02:12:03,170 --> 02:12:04,400
换行头了啊
Ah, a costume change!

1573
02:12:08,480 --> 02:12:10,140
诶 多谢大伙来看我
Thank you all for coming to see me.

1574
02:12:10,630 --> 02:12:12,220
没事了 我好了
I'm fine now.

1575
02:12:12,340 --> 02:12:13,480
说得轻巧
Sounds easy now.

1576
02:12:14,460 --> 02:12:15,710
没见遭罪的时候呢
You didn't see him suffer!

1577
02:12:15,800 --> 02:12:17,140
蝶衣 起来吧
Dieyi,

1578
02:12:17,140 --> 02:12:17,740
起来吧
get out of bed.

1579
02:12:17,740 --> 02:12:20,620
全北京的大街小巷 都支愣着耳朵
All of Peking is waiting with bated breath

1580
02:12:20,780 --> 02:12:23,390
等着听霸王和虞姬出场呐
for the next appearance of the king and his Concubine!

1581
02:12:24,260 --> 02:12:27,540
什么叫“盛代元音”呐 这他妈就是
It'll be the goddamn golden hit of a golden era.

1582
02:12:35,570 --> 02:12:36,890
大家让我说几句
You've asked me to say a few words.

1583
02:12:37,180 --> 02:12:39,520
那我就说几句 说不好
I'm not sure how to put it.

1584
02:12:41,950 --> 02:12:42,760
现代戏
I think these modern operas...

1585
02:12:44,610 --> 02:12:45,390
有意思
...are interesting,

1586
02:12:46,680 --> 02:12:48,080
可现代戏的服装
but the costumes...

1587
02:12:48,480 --> 02:12:49,440
有点怪
...aren't very attractive.

1588
02:12:50,240 --> 02:12:51,450
不如行头好看
The backdrops are also too realistic,

1589
02:12:52,280 --> 02:12:53,770
布景也太实
nothing pleasures the eye.

1590
02:12:54,820 --> 02:12:56,890
京戏讲究的 是个情境
Yet Peking Opera puts great value on ambience.

1591
02:12:57,420 --> 02:12:59,600
唱 念 做 打
Song, recital, movement and acrobatics...

1592
02:12:59,930 --> 02:13:01,310
都在这个情境里面
...are part of this ambience.

1593
02:13:03,770 --> 02:13:06,030
穿上这一身 往布景前头一站
But if you're wearing outfits like these and standing...

1594
02:13:07,570 --> 02:13:09,410
玩艺再好 也不对头了
...in front of those backdrops, it just doesn't work.

1595
02:13:10,830 --> 02:13:14,120
我就怕 这么弄 就不是京戏了
I fear that this will be the end of opera, as we know it.

1596
02:13:15,410 --> 02:13:16,330
你们说呢
What do all of you think?

1597
02:13:22,570 --> 02:13:23,620
怎么现代戏
Are you saying that modern operas...

1598
02:13:24,380 --> 02:13:25,780
就不是京戏了
...aren't Peking Opera?

1599
02:13:26,290 --> 02:13:27,480
京戏是什么
What is Peking Opera after all?

1600
02:13:28,200 --> 02:13:29,210
就是八个字
You can put it succinctly.

1601
02:13:29,470 --> 02:13:30,600
无声不歌
No sound but is a song,

1602
02:13:31,080 --> 02:13:32,200
无动不舞
no movement but is a dance.

1603
02:13:33,140 --> 02:13:34,780
得好看 美
It must have beauty.

1604
02:13:35,580 --> 02:13:36,460
比方说啊
For instance...

1605
02:13:36,820 --> 02:13:37,860
- 这个... - 师傅
- This... - Teacher,

1606
02:13:38,820 --> 02:13:40,030
我没听明白
I don't get it.

1607
02:13:42,930 --> 02:13:44,670
等你流上 三船五车的汗
Practise. When you've sweated enough to fill buckets,

1608
02:13:45,320 --> 02:13:46,160
就明白了
you'll get it.

1609
02:13:46,970 --> 02:13:48,330
我还是不明白
I still don't understand.

1610
02:13:48,330 --> 02:13:49,010
四儿
Xiao Si!

1611
02:13:50,350 --> 02:13:51,440
我就是不明白
I just don't get it.

1612
02:13:52,140 --> 02:13:54,210
为什么古时候的英雄美人上了台
When ancient heroes and beauties take the stage,

1613
02:13:54,320 --> 02:13:55,230
就是京戏
why should it be Peking Opera?

1614
02:13:55,660 --> 02:13:58,360
现在劳动人民上了台 就不是京戏了
but not when the labouring masses do?

1615
02:13:59,260 --> 02:14:01,100
你这...说的是两码事
You're talking apples and pears.

1616
02:14:01,330 --> 02:14:02,520
- 放肆  - 你什么态度
- Upstart! - What's this attitude?

1617
02:14:06,400 --> 02:14:07,150
段师傅
Teacher Duan,

1618
02:14:08,010 --> 02:14:08,790
您说说
I'd like to hear from you.

1619
02:14:08,990 --> 02:14:09,700
小楼
Xiaolou!

1620
02:14:18,060 --> 02:14:19,170
外边要下雨了
It's raining.

1621
02:14:19,960 --> 02:14:20,720
给你伞
I've brought your umbrella.

1622
02:14:22,320 --> 02:14:23,060
接着
Catch!

1623
02:14:31,780 --> 02:14:32,420
得
Yes,

1624
02:14:32,880 --> 02:14:33,600
知道了
yes,

1625
02:14:34,600 --> 02:14:35,340
家去吧
run along home now.

1626
02:14:50,180 --> 02:14:52,900
一提这论理的事儿 我头就大
Discussions about ethics give me a headache.

1627
02:14:54,890 --> 02:14:55,760
依我看啊
I say...

1628
02:14:56,740 --> 02:14:58,620
只要是唱这西皮二黄
if it uses the traditional musical forms,

1629
02:14:59,460 --> 02:15:00,720
它就是京戏
then it's Peking Opera.

1630
02:15:02,300 --> 02:15:03,020
是不是
Am I right?

1631
02:15:04,200 --> 02:15:04,820
小楼
Xiaolou.

1632
02:15:04,980 --> 02:15:06,790
我...我发两句言 啊
I'd like to say something.

1633
02:15:10,600 --> 02:15:13,680
自打把这戏院 啊 交给咱们国家
I've been part of the New Society since giving...

1634
02:15:14,460 --> 02:15:15,660
咱就都是新人了
...my theatre to the state.

1635
02:15:17,790 --> 02:15:19,190
程同志 也不对
Comrade Cheng, I believe you're wrong.

1636
02:15:22,580 --> 02:15:24,430
这现代戏 它是个新事
Modern opera is a new venture,

1637
02:15:25,060 --> 02:15:28,180
咱们应当拥护啊 应当支持啊
it deserves our support.

1638
02:15:34,860 --> 02:15:36,540
功也不练 嗓也不吊
You never practise.

1639
02:15:36,900 --> 02:15:38,430
耍贫顶嘴 你倒学成了
If opera relied on being a smartass, you'd graduate with honours.

1640
02:15:39,080 --> 02:15:40,340
唱戏的不靠这个
Opera requires practice,

1641
02:15:40,680 --> 02:15:43,250
凭的是功夫 本事 玩艺儿
skill and talent.

1642
02:15:44,280 --> 02:15:45,450
没你的近道儿可走
There are no shortcuts!

1643
02:15:46,210 --> 02:15:47,020
罚我跪
By forcing me to kneel,

1644
02:15:47,790 --> 02:15:48,600
你犯法
you're breaking the law.

1645
02:15:49,780 --> 02:15:52,380
不罚 不罚你永远是下三滥
And if I don't punish you, you'll always be third-rate.

1646
02:15:52,820 --> 02:15:53,780
还想成角儿
You want to be a great actor?

1647
02:15:53,930 --> 02:15:54,700
做梦
Dream on!

1648
02:15:57,440 --> 02:16:01,560
没错 你领我来 哪儿是想让我成角儿
And when did you ever seriously want me to succeed?

1649
02:16:02,490 --> 02:16:04,010
你是想找个小力笨儿
All you've ever wanted is a coolie,

1650
02:16:04,620 --> 02:16:05,750
小催帮儿
a stage hand...

1651
02:16:06,210 --> 02:16:08,520
小跟包 小腿子 小龙套
a follower, a dogsbody, a bit player!

1652
02:16:09,120 --> 02:16:10,860
你放肆 你大胆
How dare you!

1653
02:16:11,200 --> 02:16:12,400
我让你胡说八道
You're speaking absolute rubbish!

1654
02:16:12,480 --> 02:16:14,010
胡说八道 胡说八道
You're speaking absolute rubbish!

1655
02:16:19,150 --> 02:16:20,180
还不给我跪下
Kneel down!

1656
02:16:23,010 --> 02:16:23,720
师傅
Master,

1657
02:16:26,680 --> 02:16:28,180
永没那日子啦
You won't live to see the day!

1658
02:16:38,160 --> 02:16:39,010
四儿
Xiao Si!

1659
02:16:51,870 --> 02:16:52,640
滚吧
Piss off then!

1660
02:16:53,130 --> 02:16:54,890
一辈子跑你的龙套去吧
Be a bit player your whole life!

1661
02:17:01,050 --> 02:17:01,880
程老板
Mr Cheng...

1662
02:17:03,280 --> 02:17:06,600
您这话要搁在旧社会说
I can hardly...

1663
02:17:08,040 --> 02:17:08,880
我信
...believe this...

1664
02:17:10,650 --> 02:17:14,840
在新社会说 我不信
It's like something out of the Old Society!

1665
02:17:16,720 --> 02:17:18,300
我要是再跑龙套
If I continue to get bit parts,

1666
02:17:19,700 --> 02:17:21,250
对不起您的栽培
I'll be unworthy of your patronage!

1667
02:18:07,580 --> 02:18:08,420
这么说
So,

1668
02:18:10,040 --> 02:18:10,900
你知道
you know?

1669
02:18:11,250 --> 02:18:11,980
啊
What?

1670
02:18:12,420 --> 02:18:13,640
啊 嘿嘿
Yes. Uh.

1671
02:18:13,820 --> 02:18:14,880
这 我这
Uh, I...

1672
02:18:15,230 --> 02:18:16,840
诶 我也是刚刚才知道
Uh, I just learned myself...

1673
02:18:16,840 --> 02:18:17,780
不对吧
That's not true,

1674
02:18:18,770 --> 02:18:19,690
段师傅
Teacher Duan.

1675
02:18:20,480 --> 02:18:23,470
昨儿开会 您可是在场的啊
You were there at the meeting last night.

1676
02:18:28,650 --> 02:18:30,840
你说的 你去通知 蝶衣换角儿嘛
But you said you'd notify Dieyi that you were replacing him.

1677
02:18:31,400 --> 02:18:32,100
啊
Ah.

1678
02:18:32,240 --> 02:18:33,700
可后来我觉着
I had second thoughts.

1679
02:18:34,270 --> 02:18:36,380
这话 您说最合适
I decided you should tell him.

1680
02:18:36,990 --> 02:18:38,300
您同意了嘛
Don't you agree?

1681
02:18:39,450 --> 02:18:41,310
这话您都不说
If you couldn't tell him,

1682
02:18:41,640 --> 02:18:43,260
还有谁能说呀
who could?

1683
02:18:47,560 --> 02:18:48,220
掭了
Take it off!

1684
02:18:50,370 --> 02:18:51,060
掭了
Take it off!

1685
02:18:51,200 --> 02:18:53,490
赶快唱啦 师哥 您别这样
Don't. Don't be like that!

1686
02:18:53,670 --> 02:18:54,450
师哥
Bro.

1687
02:18:54,450 --> 02:18:55,520
我他妈的不唱了
I won't fucking sing anymore!

1688
02:18:56,100 --> 02:18:57,280
谁爱唱 谁唱去
Let whoever wants to perform do so.

1689
02:18:57,390 --> 02:18:59,460
赶快唱啦 师哥 您别走
Don't. Don't be like that!

1690
02:18:59,850 --> 02:19:00,500
小楼
Xiaolou,

1691
02:19:00,600 --> 02:19:01,800
小楼 你不能走
Xiaolou, you mustn't go.

1692
02:19:08,980 --> 02:19:10,310
段小楼同志
Comrade Duan,

1693
02:19:16,650 --> 02:19:19,550
而今台下坐的 可都是劳动人民
that audience is made up of the Iabou ring masses.

1694
02:19:20,690 --> 02:19:24,850
唱不唱 您自个儿掂量着
You decide for yourself whether or not to sing for them.

1695
02:19:40,520 --> 02:19:42,760
小楼 虞姬都上了
Xiaolou, the concubine's on stage.

1696
02:19:43,090 --> 02:19:44,270
你该盯场了
You'd better hurry.

1697
02:19:47,940 --> 02:19:48,680
小楼
Xiaolou...

1698
02:19:50,400 --> 02:19:51,140
段老板
Mr Duan!

1699
02:19:51,580 --> 02:20:02,760
“自从我随大王东征西战”
I've followed my king on his military campaigns

1700
02:20:12,580 --> 02:20:26,260
“受风霜与劳碌年复年年”
Enduring the wind and frost, and hard toil year after year

1701
02:20:29,960 --> 02:20:32,540
“恨只恨”
I hate only the lawless tyrant,

1702
02:20:32,840 --> 02:20:57,310
“无道秦把生灵涂炭”
who has plunged our people, into an abyss of misery!

1703
02:21:07,660 --> 02:21:22,080
“只害得众百姓困苦颠连”
The people have suffered untold hardship and pain

1704
02:21:22,080 --> 02:21:26,600
“大王回营啊”
The king has returned to camp!

1705
02:21:28,260 --> 02:21:33,970
“来也”
I'm here

1706
02:21:41,790 --> 02:21:44,390
“大王”
My king!

1707
02:21:52,800 --> 02:22:02,560
“此一番连累你 多受惊慌”
I've caused you so much grief

1708
02:22:03,070 --> 02:22:04,540
多谢菊仙小姐
Thank you very much, Miss Juxian.

1709
02:22:18,240 --> 02:22:19,010
蝶衣
Dieyi!

1710
02:22:22,270 --> 02:22:23,520
蝶衣 你开开门
Dieyi, open the door! Open up!

1711
02:22:24,730 --> 02:22:25,490
蝶衣
Dieyi!

1712
02:22:30,600 --> 02:22:33,330
师哥给你赔不是 还不成吗
Won't you accept my apology?

1713
02:22:41,340 --> 02:22:43,280
那条小蛇 可是你把它捂活的
That little snake you rescued...

1714
02:22:45,240 --> 02:22:46,940
而今人家 已然修练成龙啦
...has turned into a veritable dragon!

1715
02:22:47,440 --> 02:22:48,300
不顺着他
You have to go along with it!

1716
02:22:51,170 --> 02:22:52,860
不顺着他 能成吗
You have to go along with it! What else can you do?

1717
02:22:55,100 --> 02:22:58,240
这戏总得唱吧 这可是你说的
No matter what, as you told me, you have to keep on singing!

1718
02:22:59,130 --> 02:23:00,260
你也不出来看看
Come on out and see what's playing...

1719
02:23:00,500 --> 02:23:02,330
这世上的戏 都唱到哪一出了
...in the theatre of life these days.

1720
02:23:07,400 --> 02:23:08,590
小豆子
Douzi,

1721
02:23:09,250 --> 02:23:10,860
你就听师哥一句
listen to your stage brother.

1722
02:23:11,130 --> 02:23:12,020
服个软
Go with the times!

1723
02:23:12,490 --> 02:23:14,260
那还不是我的霸王 你的虞姬呀
I'll still be the king and you my concubine!

1724
02:23:17,080 --> 02:23:19,360
虞姬 为什么要死
Why does the concubine have to die?

1725
02:23:25,360 --> 02:23:26,140
蝶衣啊
Dieyi,

1726
02:23:27,880 --> 02:23:31,130
你可真是不疯魔 不成活呀
Dieyi, why are you so impossible?

1727
02:23:33,920 --> 02:23:35,240
可那是戏
That's the play, for heaven's sake.

1728
02:24:55,080 --> 02:24:57,110
“中央人民广播电台”
Central People's Radio will now broadcast

1729
02:24:58,720 --> 02:25:02,100
